hadiths[182]{hadithnumber,text}:
4519,"Yahya-bin-Yahya tamimi ne kaha : Saleem bin akhzar ne hamein Ibne-Aun se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine qitaal se pahley (Islam ki) dawat dene ke barey mein poochhney ke liye Naafe ko khat likha. kaha : to unhon-ne mujhey jawab likha : ye shuru Islam mein tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Banu-Mustaliq par hamla kya jabke wo be-khabar they aur unke maweshi pani pi rahe they, aap ne unke jangju afraad ko qatl kya aur jang na karne ke qaabil logon ko qaidi banaya aur aapko us din. Yahya ne kaha : mera khayal hai, unhon-ne kaha : Juweriya . ya qateiyat se binte-Haaris kaha, milein. mujhey ye hadis Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan ki aur wo us lashkar mein maujood they."
4520,"ibne-abi Adi ne Ibne-Aun se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki aur unhon-ne Juweriya binte-Haaris (Raziallahu anhu) kaha, shak nahi kya."
4521,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba ne kaha : hamein Wakee-bin-Jarraah ne Sufiyan se hadis bayan ki, neez Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim ne kaha : hamein yahya-bin-Aadam ne khabar di, kaha : hamein Sufiyan ne khabar di, kaha : ye hadis unhon-ne hamein imlaa karwaai."
4522,"neez Abdullah-bin Hashim ne kaha, padhi. alfaz unhi ke hain. padhi. mujhey Abdur-Rehman-bin-Mehdi ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Sufiyan ne Alqama bin-Marsad se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Sulaiman-bin-Barida se aur unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab kisi badey lashkar ya chhotey dastey par kisi ko ameer muqarrar kartey to usey khas uski apni zaat ke barey mein Allah se darney ki aur un tamam musalmanon ke barey mein, jo uske sath hain, bhalai ki talqeen kartey, phir farmatey : Allah ke naam se Allah ki raah mein jihad karo, jo Allah Taala se kufr kartey hain unse lado, na khayanat karo, na bad-ehdi karo, na musla karo aur na kisi bachchey ko qatl karo aur jab mushrikon mein se apne dushman se takraao to unhein teen baton ki taraf bulao , unmein se jisey wo taslim kar lein, (usi ko) unki taraf se qabool kar lo aur un ( par hamley ( se ruk jao. unhein Islam ki dawat do, agar wo maan lein to usey un (ki taraf ( se qabool kar lo aur (jang se) ruk jao, phir unhein apne ilaaqey se muhajireen ke ilaaqey mein aa janey ki dawat do aur unhein bataao ke agar wo aisa karengey to unke liye wahi huquq hongey jo muhajireen ke hain aur un par wahi zimmedariyaan hongi jo muhajireen par hain. agar wo wahan se naqle-makaani karne par inkar karein to unhein bataao ke phir wo baadiya-nasheen musalmanon ki tarah hongey, un par Allah ka wahi hukm Nafiz hoga jo mominon par Nafiz hota hai aur ghaneemat aur fai mein se unke liye kuchh na hoga magar is sura mein ke wo musalmanon ke sath mil kar jihad karein. agar wo inkar karein to unse jiziye ka mutalba karo, agar wo taslim kar lein to unki taraf se qabool kar lo aur ruk jao aur agar wo inkar karein to Allah se madad maango aur unse lado aur jab tum kisi qiley (mein rehney) walon ka muhaasra karo aur wo tum se chaahein ke tum unhein Allah aur uske Nabi ka ehado-paimaan ata karo to unhein Allah aur uske Nabi ka ehdo-paimaan na do balke apni aur apne sathiyon ki taraf se ehad w amaan do, kyonke ye baat ke tum log apne aur apne sathiyon ke ahado-paimaan ki khilaf-warzi kar baitho, iski nisbat halki hai ke tum Allah aur uske rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka ahado-paimaan tod 2 aur jab tum qila band logon ka muhaasra karo aur wo tum se chaahein ke tum unhein Allah ke hukm par (qiley se) nichey utarney do to unhein Allah ke hukm par nichey na utarney do balke apne hukm par unhein nichey utaaro kyonke tumhen malum nahi ke tum unke barey mein Allah ke sahi hukm par pahunch patey ho ya nahi. ( ibne- Hisham ne kaha : ( Abdur-Rehman ne yahi kaha ya isi tarah kaha, Ishaq ne apni hadis ke aakhir mein ye izafa kya : yahya-bin-Aadam se riwayat hai ke) Alqama ne) kaha : maine ye hadis muqaatil bin Hayyan se bayan ki. padhi. Yahya ne kaha : yani Alqama ne ibne- hayyan se bayan ki. padhi. to unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Muslim-bin Haisam ne Hazrat Nauman bin Muqrin (Raziallahu anhu) ke waastey se Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se isi tarah hadis bayan ki."
4523,"Abdus-Samad bin Abdul-Waris ne mujhey hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Shoba ne hadis sunai, kaha : mujhey Alqama bin-Marsad ne hadis bayan ki ke unhein Sulaiman-bin-Barida ne apne walid se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab kisi ameer ko ya chhotey lashkar ko rawaana kartey to aap usey bulatey aur talqeen farmatey. padhi. phir unhon ( Shoba ( ne Sufiyan ki hadis ke ham mana hadis bayan ki."
4524,Husain-bin-Waleed ne Shoba se yahi hadis riwayat ki.
4525,"Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne sathiyon mein se kisi ko jab apne kisi mamley ki zimme-dari de kar rawana kartey to farmatey : khushkhabri do, door na bhagaao, aasani paida karo aur mushkil mein na dalo ."
4526,"Shoba ne Saeed bin abi Burda se, unhon-ne apne walid ke hawale se apne dada (hazrat abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein aur Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ko Yaman ki taraf bheja aur farmaya : tum donon aasani paida karna, mushkil mein na daalna, khushkhabri dena, door na bhagaana, aapas mein ittifaq rakhna, ikhtilaf na karna."
4527,"Amr aur Zaid-bin-abi-Unaisa donon ne Saeed bin abi Burda se riwayat ki, unhon-ne apne walid se ( aagey ( apne dada se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Shoba ki hadis ki tarah riwayat ki. aur Zaid-bin-abii-Unaisaa ki hadis mein ye nahi hai : donon aapas mein ittifaq rakhna aur ikhtilaf na karna."
4528,"Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aasani karo, dushwari paida na karo, itminan dilao aur door na bhagaao ."
4529,"Ubaidullah ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : qiyamat ke din Allah jab pahley aaney walon aur baad mein aaney walon ko jama karega to bad-ahdi karne waley har shakhs ke liye aik jhanda buland kya jaeyga aur kaha jaeyga : ye falan bin falan ki bad-ahdi (ka nishan ( hai."
4530,"Ayub aur sakhr bin Juweriya donon ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se yahi hadis bayan ki."
4531,"Abdullah-bin-Dinar se riwayat hai, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : bad-ahdi karne waley ke liye qiyamat ke din Allah aik jhanda nasab karega aur kaha jaeyga : suno! ye falan ki ahad shikani (ka nishan) hai."
4532,"Abdullah (bin umr (Raziallahu anhu)) ke 2 beton Hamza aur Salim se riwayat hai ke Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they : har ehad shikan ke liye qiyamat ke din aik jhanda hoga."
4533,"Muhammad-bin Ibrahim ibne-abi Adi aur Muhammad-bin-Jafar donon ne Shoba se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Sulaiman (Aamash) se, unhon-ne abu-Waeil se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (bin Masood) (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, aap ne farmaya : har ahad shikan ke liye qiyamat ke din aik jhanda hoga, kaha jaeyga : ye falan ki ehad shikani (ka nishan) hai."
4534,Nazar-bin-Shumail aur Abdur-Rehman (bin Mehdi ( ne Shoba se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki aur Abdur-Rehman ki hadis mein ye (alfaz ( nahi hain : kaha jaeyga : ye falan ki ahad shikani (ka nishan ( hai
4535,"Yazeed bin Abdul-Azeez ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Shaqiq se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : har ehad shikan ke liye qiyamat ke din aik jhanda hoga, wo uske zariey se pehchaana jaeyga, kaha jaeyga : ye falan ki bad-ehdi (ka nishan) hai."
4536,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : har ehad shikan ke liye qiyamat ke din aik jhanda hoga jis se wo pehchaana jaeyga."
4537,"Khulaid ne abu-Nazara se, unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, aap ne farmaya : bad-ehdi karne waley har shakhs ke liye, qiyamat ke din uske pichhey aik jhanda (nasab) hoga."
4538,"Mustamir bin Rayyan ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein abu-Nazara ne Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ahad shikani karne waley har shakhs ke liye qiyamat ke din aik jhanda hoga jo uski bad-ahdii ke baqadr buland kya jaeyga, suno ! ehad shikani mein koi Awam ke) ahad shikan ( ameer se bada nahi hoga."
4539,Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jang aik chaal hai.
4540,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jang ( dushman ko) dhokey (main rakhney) ka naam hai."
4541,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : dushman se muqaabley ki tamanna mat karo, lekin jab tumhara unse muqaabla ho to sabr karo."
4542,"abu-Nazar se riwayat hai, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sathiyon mein se qabila Aslam ke aik aadmi , jinhein Abdullah-bin-abi-Ufa (Raziallahu anhu) kaha jata tha, ke khat se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Umar-bin Ubaidullah ko , jab unhon-ne (jihad ki gharaz se) harooriya ki taraf kooch kya, ye bataaney ke liye khat likha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne kuchh dinon ( jang ( mein, jin mein aap ka dushman se muqaabla hota, intizar kartey, yahan tak ke jab suraj dhal jata, aap un ( sathiyon (ke darmyan khadey hotey aur farmatey : logo! dushman se muqaabley ki tamanna mat karo aur Allah se aafiyat maango, (lekin) jab tum unka saamnaa karo to sabr karo aur jaan rakho ke jannat talwaaron ke saaey ke nichey hai. phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey huey aur farmaya : aey Allah ! kitab ko utaarney waale, badalon ko chalaney waley aur lashkaron ko shikast dene waley! unhein shikast de aur hamein un par nusrat (madad) ata farma."
4543,"Khalid-bin-Abdullah ne hamein Ismail bin abi Khalid se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-abi-Ufa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (Madina par hamley karne waale) lashkaron ke khilaf ye dua ki : aey Allah ! kitab ko utaarney waley! jald hisab karne waley! sab lashkaron ko shikast de, aey Allah! unhein shikast de aur unke qadam larzaa de."
4544,"Wakee bin-Jarrah ne hamein Ismail-bin-abi Khalid se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine ibne-abi-Ufa (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dua ki. padhi. ( aagey ( Khalid ki hadis ki tarah hai, albatta unhon-ne (aey ( lashkaron ko shikast dene waley ke alfaz kahey aur aap ke farman ( اللهم (ka zikr nahi kya."
4545,"Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim aur ibne-abi-Umar ne ibne-Uena se, unhon-ne Ismail se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki aur ibne-abi-Umar ne apni riwayat mein badalon ko chalaney waley ke alfaz ka izafa kya."
4546,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke) jange-) Uhud ke din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( baar-baar ( ye farma rahe they : aey Allah! agar to ye chahta hai to ( aaj ke baad) zamin main teri ibadat na ki jaeygi. (teri ibadat karne wali aakhiri ummat khatm ho jaeygi.)
4547,"Leis ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke aik ghazwey mein aik aurat maqtool mili to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aurton aur bachchon ke qatl par) sakht ( na-gawari ka izhar kya (aur us se mana farma diya. ("
4548,"Ubaidullah-bin-Umar ne hamein Naafe ke hawale se Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : jangon mein se aik jang mein aik aurat maqtool mili to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aurton aur bachchon ke qatl se mana farma diya."
4549,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne hamein Zohri se khabar di, unhon-ne Ubaidullah se, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Sa'b-bin-Jassama (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se mushrekeen ke gharaaney ke barey mein puchha gaya, un par hamla kiya jata hai to wo (hamla karne waale) unki aurton aur bachchon ko bhi nuqsan pahuncha detey hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : wo unhi mein se hain."
4550,"Mamar ne hamein Zohri se khabar di, unhon-ne Ubaidullah-bin-Abdullaah-bin-Utba se, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Sa'b bin Jassama (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! shab khoon mein ham mushrekeen ki aurton aur bachchon ko nuqsan pahuncha detey hain. aap ne farmaya : wo unhi mein se hain."
4551,"Amr-bin-Dinar ne mujhey khabar di ke unhein ibne-Shahab ne Ubaidullah-bin-Abdullaah-bin-Utba se khabar di, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Sa'b bin Jassama (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha gaya ke agar kuchh ghud-sawar raat ko dhaawa bolein aur mushrikon ke (sath unke kuchh) beton ko (bhi) qatl kar dein (to gunah to nahi hai?) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : wo apne baap-dada hi mein se hain."
4552,"Yahya-bin-Yahya, Muhammad-bin Rumeh aur Qutaiba-bin-Saeed ne Leis se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Naafe se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne banu-Nazeer ke khajoor ke darakht jalaaey aur kaat daley aur ye buwera ka maqam tha (jahan ye darakht waaqe they Quteba aur ibne-Rumeh ne apni hadis mein ye izafa kya : is par izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne ye aayat nazil farmai : tum ne khajoor ka jo darakht kaat daala ya usey apni judun par khada chhod diya to wo Allah ki ijazat se tha aur isliye taake wo ( Allah ( naafarmaanon ko ruswa kare."
4553,"Musa-bin-Aqba ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne banu-Nazeer ke khajooron ke darakht kaatey aur jalaa diye. usi ke barey mein Hazrat Hassan (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : banu-Lui ( Quraish) ke sardaaron ke liye buwera mein har taraf phailney wali aag ki koi haisiyat na thii.' aur usi ke barey mein ye aayat nazil hui : tum ne khajoor ka jo bhi darakht kaata ya usey chhod diya. aayat ke aakhir tak."
4554,"Ubaidullah ne Naafe se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne banu-Nazeer ki khajooron ke darakht jala dene."
4555,"Hammam-bin-Munabba se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : ye ( hadison ( hain jo hamein Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan kin, phir unhon-ne chand hadisein bayan kin, unmein se (eik ( ye hai : aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : anbiya mein se kisi Nabi ne jihad kya to unhon-ne apni qaum se kaha : mere sath wo aadmi na aaey jisne kisi aurat se shadi ki hai, wo uske sath shabe-zufaaf guzaarna chahta hai aur abhi tak nahi guzari, na wo jisne ghar tameer kya hai aur abhi tak uski chhatein buland nahi kin aur na wo jisne bakriyan ya haamla oontniyan kharidi hain aur wo unke bachcha dene ka muntazir hai. kaha : wo jihad ke liye nikley, namaze-Asr ke waqt ya iske qareeb , wo basti ke nazdeek pahunchey to unhon-ne suraj se kaha : to bhi) Allah ke hukm ka ( paaband hai aur main bhi paaband hon, aey Allah ! usey kuchh waqt ke liye mujh par rok de. to usey rok diya gaya, yahan tak ke Allah ne unhein fateh di. kaha : unhein ghaneemat mein jo mila, unhon-ne usko ikattha kar liya, aag usey khaney ke liye aai to usey khaney se baaz rahi. is par unhon-ne kaha : tumharey darmyan khayanat (ka irtikaab hua) hai, har qabeeley ka aik aadmi meri bait kare. unhon-ne unki bait ki to aik aadmi ka hath unke hath se chimat gaya. unhon-ne kaha : khayanat tum logon mein hui hai, lihaza tumhara qabila meri bait kare. us qabeeley ne unki bait ki to (aap ka hath ( 2 ya teen aadmiyon ke hath se chimat gaya. is par unhon-ne kaha : khayanat tum mein hai, tum ne khayanat ki hai. kaha : to wo gaaey ke sar ke jitna sona nikal kar unke paas ley aaey. kaha : unhon-ne usey maale-ghanimat mein rakha, wo buland jagah par rakha hua tha, to aag aai aur usey kha gaee. amwaale-ghaneemat ham se pahley kisi ke liye halal na they, ye ( hamarey liye halal) us wjah se hua ke Allah tabarak w taala ne hamari kamzori aur ajz ko dekha to usne unko hamarey liye halal kar diya."
4556,"abu-Awana ne Samak se, unhon-ne Musab-bin-Sad se aur unhon-ne apne walid (hazrat Sad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mere walid ne khums mein se koi cheez li, usey lekar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaey aur kaha : ye mujhey hiba farma dein to aap ne inkar kya. kaha : is par izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne (ye hukm ( nazil farmaya : log aap se amwaale-ghaneemat ke barey mein poochhtey hain, keh dijiye : amwaale-ghaneemat Allah ke liye aur rasool ke liye hain."
4557,"Shoba ne hamein Samak-bin-Harab se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Musab-bin-Sad se aur unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mere barey mein char aayatein nazil huin : mujhey aik talwaar mili, (phir kaha :) wo usey lekar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur kaha : Allah ke rasool! (apne hissey ke ilawa) ye talwaar mujhey mazeed ata farma dein. to aap ne farmaya : usey rakh do. wo phir uthey aur kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! (ye talwaar ( mujhey mazeed de dein. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya : jahan se li hai wahin rakh do. wo phir uthey aur kaha : Allah ke rasool! (apne hissey ke ilawa ( ye bhi mujhey inayat farma dein. to aap ne farmaya : usey rakh do. wo phir uthey aur kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! (apne hissey ke ilawa ( ye mujhey inayat farma dein. kya main us shakhs jaisa qarar diya jaaunga jiske liye (jang mein) koi fayda nahi hua? to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se farmaya : tum ne usey jahan se liya hai wahin rakh do. kaha : is par ye aayat nazil hui : wo aap se ghaneematon ke barey mein poochhtey hain. keh dijiye! ghaneematein Allah ke liye aur rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye hain."
4558,"Imam Malik ne Naafe se aur unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Najad ki taraf aik dasta bheja, main bhi unmein tha, unhon-ne bahut se oont ghaneemat mein hasil kiye to unka hissey baara baara oont ya gyara (11) gyara oont tha aur unhein eik-eik oont zayed diya gaya tha."
4559,"Leis ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Najad ki taraf aik dasta bheja , unmein ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bhi they, unke hissey baara baara oont tak pahunch gaey aur iske ilawa unhein eik-eik oont zayed (bhi) mila to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us (faisley) ko tabdeel nahi kya."
4560,"Ali-bin-Mus-hir aur abdur-Raheem bin Sulaiman ne Ubaidullah-bin-Umar se, unhon-ne Naafe se aur unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Najad ki taraf aik dasta bheja, main bhi usmein gaya. hamein oont aur bakriyan milin to hamarey hissey baara-baara oonton tak pahunch gaey aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein eik-eik oont zayed bhi diya."
4561,Yahya qattaan ne Ubaidullah se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki.
4562,"Ayub ne hamein hadis bayan ki, aur (eik dusri sanad se) Ibne-Aun ne kaha : maine ghaneemat ke barey mein poochhney ke liye Naafe ki taraf khat likha , unhon-ne mujhey jawab bhi likha ke Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) dastey mein they. neez Musa aur Usama-bin-Zaid ne bhi hadis bayan ki, un sab ( Ayub , Ibne-Aun , Musa aur Usama ( ne Naafe se isi sanad ke sath unhi ki hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki."
4563,"Abdullah-bin-Rijaa ne Yunus se, unhon-ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Salim se aur unhon-ne apne walid (hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein khums se hamarey hissey ke siwa izaafi bhi diya to mujhey aik shaarif mila. padhi. aur shaarif se murad pukhta umr ka (mazboot ( oont hai."
4564,"ibne-Mubarak aur ibne- Wahab donon ne Yunus ke hawale se Zohri se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se ye hadis pahunchi , unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik dastey ko zayed diya. ibne- -Rijaa ki hadis ki tarah ."
4565,"Aqeel-bin-Khalid ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Salim se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kabhi-kabhi aam lashkar ki taqseem se hat kar kuchh daston ko, jinhein aap rawaana farmatey they, khususi taur par unke liye zayed atiyaat detey they, aur khums un sab muhimon mein wajib tha."
4566,"Hushaim ne Yahya-bin-Saeed se, unhon-ne Umar-bin Kasir bin Aflah se aur unhon-ne abu-Muhammad Ansari se riwayat ki aur wo Hazrat abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) ke ham nasheeni they, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, padhi. aur unhon ( abu-Muhammad ( ne hadis bayan ki."
4567,"Leis ne Yahya-bin-Saeed se, unhon-ne Umar-bin Kasir bin Aflah se, unhon-ne abu-Muhammad jo Maula abu-Qatada ke naam se mashhoor hain, se riwayat ki ke Hazrat abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, padhi. aur hadis bayan ki."
4568,"imam Malik-bin-Anas kehtey hain : mujhey Yahya-bin-Saeed ne Umar-bin Kasir bin Aflah se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) ke Maula abu-Muhammad se aur unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Hunain ke saal ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath nikley, jab (dushman se) hamara saamna hua to musalmanon mein bhagdad machi. kaha : maine mushrikon mein se aik aadmi dekha jo musalmanon ke aik aadmi par ghalib aa gaya tha, main ghoom kar uski taraf badha yahan tak ke uske peechhey aa gaya aur uski gardan ke patthey par waar kya, wo ( usey chhod kar) meri taraf badha aur mujhey us zor se dabaaya ke mujhey us (dabaaney) se maut ki bu mehsus honey lagi, phir usko maut ne aa liya to usne mujhey chhod diya, iske baad meri Hazrat umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) se mulaqat hui, unhon-ne puchha : logon ko kya ho gaya hai? maine kaha : Allah ka hukm hai. phir log wapas paltey aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) baith gaey to aap ne farmaya : jisne kisi ko qatl kya, (aur ( uske paas uski koi daleel ( nishani wghaira) ho to us ( maqtool ( se chheena hua saaman usi ka hoga. kaha : to main khada hua aur kaha : mere haq mein kon gawahi dega? phir main baith gaya. phir aap ne isi tarah irshad farmaya, kaha : to main khada hua aur kaha : mere haq mein kon gawahi dega? phir main baith gaya. phir aap ne teesri baar yahi farmaya, kaha : main phir khada hua to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : abu-Qataada! tumhara kya mamla hai? to maine aapko ye waqia sunaya. is par logon mein se aik aadmi ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! us ne sach kaha hai. us maqtool ka chheena hua saaman mere paas hai, aap unhein unke haq se (dastbardaar honey par) mutmain kar dijiye. is par Hazrat Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : nahi, Allah ki qism ! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Allah ke sheron mein se aik sher se, jo Allah aur uske rasool ki taraf se ladai karta hai, nahi chaahengey ke wo apne maqtool ka chheena hua saman tumhen de dein. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : unhon-ne sach kaha : wo unhi ko de do. to usne (wo saman) mujhey de diya, kaha : maine (usi saaman mein se) zirah farokht ki aur us (ki qeemat ( se (apni ( banu-Salma (ki aabadi ( mein aik baagh khareed liya. wo pehla maal tha jo maine Islam (ke zamaney) mein banaya. Leis ki hadis mein hai : Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : hargiz nahi, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Allah ke sheron mein se aik sher ko chhod kar Quraish ke aik chhotey se lagad baghghey ko ata nahi karengey. Leis ki hadis mein hai : ( unhon-ne kaha ( wo pahlaa maal tha jo maine banaya."
4569,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : badr ke din jab main saf mein khada tha, maine apni daain aur baain taraf nazar daudaai to main Ansar ke 2 ladkon ke darmyan mein khada tha, unki umrein kam thin, maine aarzoo ki, kash! main un donon ki nisbat zyada taaqatwar aadmiyon ke darmyan hota, (itney mein) unmein se aik ne mujhey hath laga kar mutwajjeh kya aur kaha : chacha! kya aap abu-Jahal ko pehchantey hain? kaha : maine kaha : haan , bhatijey ! tumhen us se kya kaam hai? usne kaha : mujhey bataya gaya hai ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko bura-bhala kehta hai, us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai! agar maine usey dekh liya to mera wjood us waqt tak uske wujood se alag nahi hoga yahan tak ke ham mein se jald tar marney waley ko maut aa jaey. kaha : maine is par tajjub kya to doosrey ne mujhey mutwajjeh kya aur wahi baat kahi, kaha : phir zyada der na guzri ke meri nazar abu-Jahal par padi, wo logon mein ghoom raha tha. to maine (un donon se) kaha : tum dekh nahi rahe? ye hai tumhara (matlooba) banda jiske barey main tum poochh rahe they. kaha : wo donon yakdam uski taraf lapkey aur is par apni talwaarein barsa din yahan tak ke usey qatl kar diya, phir palat kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur aapko uski khabar di to aap ne puchha : tum donon mein se usey kis ne qatl kya hai? un donon mein se har aik ne jawab diya : maine usey qatl kya hai. aap ne puchha : kya tum donon ne apni talwaarein saaf kar li hain? unhon-ne kaha : nahi. aap ne donon talwaarein dekhin aur farmaya : tum donon ne usey qatl kya hai. aur uske saazo-saaman ka faisla aap ne Muaz bin-Amr bin jamooh (Raziallahu anhu) ke haq mein diya aur wo donon jawan Muaz bin-Amr bin jamooh aur Muaz bin Ifra (Raziallahu anhu) they"
4570,"Muawiya-bin-Saleh ne Abdur-Rehman bin Juber se, unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Auf bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Himyar ke aik aadmi ne dushman ke aik aadmi ko qatl kar diya aur uska saazo-saamaan lena chaha to Hazrat Khalid-bin Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein mana kar diya aur wo un par ameer they, chunanche Auf bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) (apne Himyari sathi ki himaayat ke liye) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaey aur aapko bataya to aap ne Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : tumhen uske maqtool ka saman usey deney se kya baat rokti hai? unhon-ne jawab diya : Allah ke rasool! maine usey zyada samjha. aap ne farmaya : wo (saman) unke hawale kar do. iske baad Hazrat Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) Hazrat Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas se guzrey to unhon-ne unki chadar kheenchi aur kaha : kya maine pura kar diya jo maine aap ke samney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hawale se kaha tha? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unki baat sun li to aapko ghussa aa gaya aur farmaya : Khalid ! usey mat do, Khalid! usey mat do. kya tum mere (muqarrar kiye huey) ameeron ko mere liye chhod saktey ho (ke main islaah karun tum taaney aur kataksh na karo! tumhari aur unki misal us aadmi ki tarah hai jisey oonton ya bakriyon ka charwaha banaya gaya, us ne unhein churaayaa, phir unko pani pilaaney ke waqt ka intizar kya aur unhein hauz par ley gaya, unhon-ne usmein se peenaa shuru kya to unhon-ne iska saaf pani pi liya aur gadla chhod diya to saaf pani tumharey liye hai aur gadlaa unka."
4571,"Safwan bin-Amr ne Abdur-Rehman bin Jubair-bin-Nufair se, unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Auf bin Malik Ashjai (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : main Mauta ki jang mein Hazrat Zaid-bin-Haarisa (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath janey walon ke sath rawaana hua, Yaman se madad ke liye aaney wala aik aadmi bhi mera rafeeqe-safar hua. unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki, albatta unhon-ne hadis mein kaha : Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine kaha : Khalid! kya aapko malum nahi tha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne salb (maqtool ke saazo-saamaan) ka faisla qaatil ke haq mein kya tha? unhon-ne kaha : kyon nahi! lekin maine usey zyada khayal kya."
4572,"Ayas bin Salma ne kaha : mujhey mere walid Hazrat Salma-bin-Akwa (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Hunain ki jang ladi, us doran mein aik baar ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath subah ka khana kha rahe they ke surkh oont par aik aadmi aaya, usey bithaya, phir us ne apne patkey se chamdey ki aik rassi nikaali aur us se oont ko baandh diya, phir wo logon ke sath khana khaney ke liye aagey badha aur jaaiza leney laga, ham mein kamzori aur hamari sawaariyon mein dublaapan maujood tha, ham mein kuchh paidal bhi they, achcha wo daudta hua nikla, apne oont ke paas aaya, uski rassi kholi, phir usey bithaya, is par Sawar hua aur usey uthaya to wo (oont) usey lekar daud pada. (ye dekh kar) khaakastri rang ki ontni par aik aadmi uske peechhey lag gaya. Hazrat Salma (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main bhi daudta hua nikla, main (peechha karne waley musalman ki) ontni ke pichhley hissey ke paas pahunch gaya, phir main aagey badha yahan tak ke oont ke pichhley hissey ke paas pahunch gaya, phir main aagey badha yahan tak ke maine oont ki nakel pakad li aur usey bitha diya, jab us ne apna ghutna zamin par rakha to maine apni talwaar nikaali aur us shakhs ke sar par waar kya to wo (gardan se) alag ho gaya, phir main oont ko nakel se chalaata hua ley aaya, is par uska paalaan aur (sawar ka ( aslaha bhi tha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne logon samet mera istiqbaal kya aur puchha is aadmi ko kis ne qatl kiya? logon ne kaha : ibne- Akwa (Raziallahu anhu) ne. aap ne farmaya : uska chheena hua saazo-saaman usi ka hai."
4573,"Hazrat Salma-bin-Akwa (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ham ne banu-Fazara se jang ladi, Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) hamarey sarbaraah they, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein hamara ameer banaya tha, jab hamarey aur chashmey ke darmyan aik ghadi ki masafat reh gaee to Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamein hukm diya aur raat ke aakhiri hissey mein ham utar padey, phir unhon-ne dhaawa bol diya aur pani par pahunch gaey, maine un logon ki aik qataar si dekhi, usmein auratein aur bachchey they, mujhey khadsha mehsus hua ke wo mujh se pahley pahaad tak pahunch jaeinge, chunanche maine unke aur pahaad ke darmyan aik teer phainka, jab unhon-ne teer dekha to thehar gaey (unhein yaqin ho gaya ke wo teer ka nishana banengey), main unhein haankta hua ley aaya, unmein banu-Fazara ki aik aurat thi, us (ke jism) par rangey huey chamdey ki chadar thi. قَشع chamdey ki bani hui chadar hoti hai. iske sath uski beti thi jo Arab ki Husain tareen ladkiyon mein se thi. maine unhein aagey lagaya yahan tak ke Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas ley aaya, unhon-ne uski beti mujhey inaam mein de di. ham Madina aaey aur maine (abhi tak) uska kapda nahi khola tha ke bazar main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se meri mulaqat hui. aap ne farmaya : Salma! wo aurat mujhey hiba kar do. maine kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! Allah ki qism ! wo mujhey bahut achi lagi hai aur (abhi tak) maine uska kapda bhi nahi khola, phir agley din bazar ( hi ( mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se meri mulaqat hui to aap ne mujh se farmaya : Salma ! wo aurat mujhey hiba kar do, Allah tumharey bap ko barkat de! maine kaha : Allah ke rasool! wo aap ke liye hai. Allah ki qasam! maine uska kapda bhi nahi khola. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey Makka bhej diya aur uske badley musalmanon mein se kuchh logon ko chhuda liya jo Makka mein qaid kiye gaey they."
4574,"Hammam-bin-Munabba se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : ye hadisein hain jo Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamein Muhammad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan kin, phir unhon-ne chand hadisein zikr kin, unmein se ye bhi thi : aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum log jis basti mein aao aur is mein qiyam karo (baghair jang ke tumhari tehweel mein aa jaey) to usmein tumharey liye (doosrey musalmanon ki tarah aik) hissa hai aur jis basti ne Allah aur uske rasool ki nafarmani ki (aur tum ne lad kar usey hasil kya) to uska khums Allah aur uske rasool ka hissa hai, phir wo (baqi sab) tumhara hai."
4575,"Qutaiba-bin-Saeed , Muhammad-bin Ibad, abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim ne hamein hadis bayan ki, alfaz ibne-Abi-Sheba ke hain. Ishaq ne kaha ke hamein khabar di, jabke dusron ne kaha ke hamein hadis bayan ki Sufiyan ne Amr se, unhon-ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Malik bin Aus se aur unhon-ne Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : banu-Nazeer ke amwaal un amwaal mein se they jo Allah ne apne rasool ko (bataur fai) ata kiye jis par musalmanon ne na ghodey daudaaey na oont . to wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye khas they. aap ( unmein se) apne ahal w ayaal ke liye aik saal ka kharch letey aur jo bach jata usey Allah ki raah mein (jihad ki) taiyaari ke liye jangi sawaariyon aur aslahey par laga detey."
4576,Mamar ne Zohri se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki.
4577,"Imam Malik ne Zohri se riwayat ki ke unhein Malik bin Aus ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne meri taraf qaasid bheja , din chadh chuka tha ke main unke paas pahuncha. kaha : maine unko unke ghar main apni charpai par baithey huey paya , unhon-ne apna jism khajoor se baney huey baan ke sath lagaya hua tha aur chamdey ke takiye se tek lagai hui thi, to unhon-ne mujh se kaha : aey maal (Malik) ! tumhari qaum mein se kuchh khandan lapaktey huey aaey they, to maine unke liye thoda sa Atiya dene ka hukm diya hai, usey lo aur unmein taqseem kar do. kaha : maine kaha : agar aap mere siwa kisi aur ko iska hukm de dein (to kaisa rahe?) unhon-ne kaha : aey maal ! tum ley lo. kaha : (itney mein unke Maula) Yarfa unke paas aaey aur kehney lagey : ameerul-momeneen ! kya aapko Usman, Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf, Zuber aur Sad (Raziallahu anhu) (ke sath milney) mein dilchaspi hai? unhon-ne kaha : haan! to usne unko ijazat di. wo andar aa gaey, wo phir aaya aur kehney laga : kya aapko Abbas aur Ali (Raziallahu anhu) (ke sath milney) mein dilchaspi hai? unhon-ne kaha : haan. to usne un donon ko bhi ijazat de di. to Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ameerul-momeneen! mere aur us jhootey, gunahgaar, ahad shikan aur khaain ke darmyan faisla kar dein. kaha : is par un logon ne kaha : haan , ameerul-momeneen ! unke darmyan faisla karke unko ( jhagdey ke azab se) raahat dila dein. padhi. Malik bin Aus ne kaha : mera khayal hai ke unhon-ne un logon ko usi gharaz se apne aagey bheja tha. padhi. to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : tum donon rukoo, main tumhen us Allah ki qism deta hun jiske hukm se aasman aur zamin qaaim hain! kya tum jantey ho ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha : hamara koi waaris nahi banega, ham jo chhodengey wo sadqa hoga? un sab ne kaha : haan. phir wo Hazrat Abbas aur Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf mutwajjeh huey aur kaha : main tum donon ko us Allah ki qism deta hun jiske hukm se aasman aur zamin qaaim hain ! kya tum donon jantey ho ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha : tumhara koi waaris nahi hoga, ham jo kuchh chhodengey, sadqa hoga? un donon ne kaha : haan. to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : bila shubah Allah Taala ne apne rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko aik khas cheez ata ki thi jo usney aap ke ilawa kisi ke liye makhsoos nahi ki thi, us ne farmaya hai : jo kuchh bhi Allah ne un bastiyon walon ki taraf se apne rasool par lautaaya wo Allah ka aur uske rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka hai. mujhey pata nahi ke unhon-ne us se pahley wali aayat bhi padhi ya nahi. padhi. unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne banu-Nazeer ke amwaal tum sab mein taqseem kar diye, Allah ki qasam! aap ne (apni zaat ko) tum par tarjeeh nahi di aur na tumhen chhod kar wo maal liya, yahan tak ke ye maal baqi bach gaya hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us se apne saal bhar ka kharch letey, phir jo baqi bach jata usey (baitul-maal ke) maal ke mutabiq (aam logon ke faaydey ke liye) istemal kartey. unhon-ne phir kaha : main tumhen us Allah ki qism deta hun jiske hukm se aasman aur zamin qaaim hain ! kya tum ye baat jantey ho? unhon-ne kaha : haan. phir unhon-ne Abbas aur Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko wahi qism di jo baqi logon ko di thi (aur kaha) : kya tum donon ye baat jantey ho? unhon-ne kaha : ji haan. phir kaha : jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) faut huey to Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka ja-nashin hun to aap donon aaey, aap apne bhatijey ki wiraasat maang rahe they aur ye apni biwi ki unke walid ki taraf se wiraasat maang rahe they. to Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha : hamara koi waaris nahi hoga, ham jo chhodengey , sadqa hai. to tum ne unhein jhoota, gunahgaar, ahad shikan aur khaain khayal kya tha aur Allah janta hai wo sachey, neku-kaar, sachchai par chalne waley aur haq ke perokar they. phir Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) faut huey aur main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ka ja-nashin bana to tum ne mujhey jhoota , gunahgaar , ahad shikan aur khaain khayal kya aur Allah janta hai ke main sachcha, neku-kaar, sachchaai par chalnewala aur haq ki pairwi karne wala hun, main iska muntazim bana, phir tum aur ye mere paas aaey, tum donon ikatthey ho aur tumhara mamla bhi aik hai. tum ne kaha : ye (amwaal) hamarey sipurd kar do. maine kaha : agar tum chaho to main is shart par ye tum donon ke hawale kar deta hun ke tum donon par Allah ke ahad ki paasdaari lazimi hogi, tum bhi usmein wahi karogey jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kartey they, to tum ne is shart par usey ley liya. unhon-ne puchha : kya aisa hi hai? un donon ne jawab diya. haan. unhon-ne kaha : phir tum ( ab ( donon mere paas aaey ho ke main tum donon ke darmyan faisla karun. nahi, Allah ki qism ! main qiyamat ke qaaim honey tak tumharey darmyan iske siwa aur faisla nahi karunga . agar tum iske intizam se aajiz ho to wo maal mujhey wapas kar do."
4578,"Mamar ne hamein Zohri se khabar di, unhon-ne Malik bin Aus bin Hadsan se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne meri taraf paigham bheja aur kaha : tumhari qaum mein se kuchh gharaanon ke log aaey they. Malik ki hadis ki tarah, albatta unhon-ne usmein kaha : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us se saal bhar apne ahal w ayaal par kharch kartey aur (hadis bayan kartey huey) kabhi-kabhi Mamar ne kaha : aap us se apne ghar walon ki saal bhar ki kam se kam khuraak alag kar letey, phir jo bachta usey Allah ke maal ( baitul-maal) ke kharch par lagaatey."
4579,"Ummul-Momenin Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat hui to aap ki beebiyon ne Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ko Hazrat Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas bhejna chaha apna tarka maangney ke liye Rasulullah ke maal se, Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha un se, kya janab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne nahi farmaya ke hamara koi waaris nahi hota, jo ham chhod jaawen wo sadqa hai."
4580,"Ummul-Momenin Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai Hazrat Fatima zohraa (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sahibzadi ne Hazrat Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas kisi ko bheja apna tarka maangney ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke un maalon mein se jo Allah Taala ne diye aapko Madina main aur fidak main aur jo kuchh bachta tha khaibar ke khums mein se. Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya hamara koi waaris nahi hota aur jo ham chhod jaawen wo sadqa hai aur Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aulad usi maal mein se khaaeygi aur main to qism khuda ki Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sadqe ko kuchh bhi nahi badloonga us haal se jaisey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane Mubarak mein tha aur main usmein wahi kaam karunga jo janab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kartey they. gharazeke Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne inkar kya Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ko kuchh dene se aur Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ko ghussa aaya unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se mulaqat chhod di aur baat na ki yahan tak ke wafat hui unki ( nauwi ne kaha ye tark mulaqat wo tark nahi jo shara' mein haram hai aur wo ye hai ke mulaqat ke waqt salam na karey ya salam ka jawab na de) aur wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke baad sirf chh mahina zinda rahin. ( kuch ne kaha aath (8) mahiney ya nau (9) mahiney ya 2 mahiney ya 70 din) bahar-haal teen taareekh Ramazan Mubarak 11 hijri muqaddas ko unhon-ne intiqal farmaya, jab unka intiqal hua to unke khawind Hazrat Ali-bin abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ne unko raat ko dafn kya aur Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko khabar na ki (is se malum hua ke raat ko dafn karna bhi jaaiz hai aur din ko afzal hai agar koi uzr na ho (aur Namaz padhi un par Hazrat Ali karamallahu wajhu ne aur jab tak Hazrat Fatima zohraa (Raziallahu anhu) zinda thin tab tak log Hazrat Ali karamallahu wajhu ki taraf maail they (b-wajah Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ke) . jab wo intiqal kar gain to Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne dekha log meri taraf se phir gaey. unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se suleh kar lena chaha aur unse bait kar lena munasib samjha aur abhi tak kai mahiney guzrey they unhon-ne bait nahi ki thi Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se to Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne Hazrat Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) ko bula bheja aur ye kelha bheja ke aap akeley aaiye aap ke sath koi na aaey, kyonke wo Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ka aana na-pasand kartey they. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Hazrat Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha qism khuda ki tum akeley unke paas na jaogey. Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha wo mere sath kya karengey qism khuda ki main to akela jaaunga . aakhir Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) unke paas gaey aur Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne tashahud padha ( jaisey khutbe ke shuru mein padhtey hain) phir kaha ham ne pehchaana aey Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) tumhari fazeelat ko aur jo Allah ne tum ko diya aur ham rashk nahi kartey us nemat par jo Allah ne tum ko di (yani khilafat aur hukumat ( lekin tum ne akeley akeley ye kaam kar liya aur ham samajhtey they ke hamara bhi haq hai is mein kyonke ham qaraabat rakhtey they Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se. phir barabar Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se baatein kartey rahe yahan tak ke Hazrat Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) ki aankhen bhar aaein . jab Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne guftgu shuru ki to kaha qism uski jiske hath mein meri jaan hai janab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki qaraabat ka lihaaz mujh ko apni qaraabat se zyada hai aur ye jo mujh main aur tum mein un baton ki baabat (yani fidak aur nazeer aur khums khaibar wghaira) ikhtilaf hua to maine haq ko nahi chhoda aur maine wo koi kaam nahi chhoda jis ko maine dekha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko kartey huey balke usko maine kya. Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha achchha aaj seh-pahar ko ham aap se bait karengey. jab Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) Zohar ki Namaz se farigh huey to member par chadhey aur tashahud padha aur Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ka qissa bayan kya aur unke der karne ka bait se aur jo uzr unhon-ne bayan kya tha wo bhi kaha phir dua ki maghfirat ki aur Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne tashahud padha aur Hazrat Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) ki fazeelat bayan ki aur ye kaha ke mera der karna bait mein is wjah se na tha ke mujh ko Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) par shak hai ya unki buzurgi aur fazeelat ka mujhey inkar hai balke ham ye samajhtey they ke is khilafat mein hamara bhi hissa hai aur Hazrat Abu-Bakar ne akeley baghair salaah ke ye kaam kar liya is wjah se hamarey dil ko ye ranj hua. ye sun kar musalman khush huey aur sab ne Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha tum ne theek kaam kya. us roz se musalman Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf maail ho gaey jab unhon-ne waajibi Amr ko ikhtiyar kya."
4581,Ummul-Momenin Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai Hazrat Fatima zohraa (Raziallahu anhu) aur Hazrat Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) donon Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaey apna hissey maangtey they Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke maal mein se aur wo us waqt talab kartey they fidak ki zamin aur khaibar ka hissa Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke maine suna hai Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se phir bayan kya hadis ko isi tarah jaisey uper guzri usmein ye hai ke phir Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) khadey huey aur Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki badaai bayan ki aur unki fazeelat aur sabqat Islam ka zikr kya phir Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaey aur unse bait ki. us waqt log Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf mutwajjeh huey aur kehney lagey aap ne theek kya aur achchha kya aur us waqt se log unke tarafdaar ho gaey jab se unhon-ne waajibii baat ko maan liya.
4582,Ummul-Momenin Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sahibzadi ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat ke baad Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se apna hissey maanga Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke tarka se jo Allah Taala ne aapko diya tha. Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne to ye farmaya hai hamara koi waaris nahi hota aur jo ham chhod jaawen wo sadqa hai aur Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat ke baad sirf chh mahiney tak zinda rahin aur wo apna hissey maangti thin khaibar aur fidak aur Madina ke sadqe mein se. Hazrat Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) ne na diya aur ye kaha ke main koi kaam jis ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kartey they chhodney wala nahi main darta hun kahin gumrah na ho jaun. phir Madina ka sadqa Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne apne zamaney mein Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) aur Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ko de diya lekin Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) par ghalba kya (yani apne qabze mein rakha) aur khaibar aur fidak ko Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne apne qabze mein rakha aur ye kaha ke ye donon sadqa they Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke jo sirf hotey aap ke huquq aur kaamon mein jo pesh aatey aapko aur ye donon iske ikhtiyar mein rahengey jo Hakim ho musalmanon ka phir aaj tak aisa hi raha (yani khaibar aur fidak hamesha khaleefa waqt ke qabze mein rahe. Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi apni khilafat mein unko taqseem nahi kya.
4583,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai Rasulullah ‌(sl) ne farmaya : merey waaris aik Dinar bhi baant nahi saktey jo chhod jaun apni aurton ke kharch ke baad aur muntazim ki ujrat ke baad bachey to wo sadqa hai.
4584,tarjama wahi jo uper 4593 main guzra .
4585,Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah ‌(sl) ne farmaya ‌ : hamara koi waaris nahi jo ham chhod jayen wo sadqa hai.
4586,"Saleem bin akhzar ne hamein Ubaidullah-bin-Umar se khabar di, kaha : hamein Naafe ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ghaneemat mein se ghodey ke liye 2 hissey aur aadmi ( sawar (ke liye aik hissey nikala."
4587,Abdullah-bin-Numair ne Ubaidullah se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki aur unhon-ne ye nahi kaha : ghaneemat mein.
4588,"abu-Zameel Samak Hanfi ne kaha : mujhey Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : jab badr ka din tha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mushrekeen ki taraf dekha, wo aik hazaar they, aur aap ke sath teen so unnees aadmi they, to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) qibla rukh huey, phir apne hath phailaey aur buland awaz se apne rab ko pukarney lagey : aey Allah ! to ne mujh se jo wada kya usey mere liye pura farma. aey Allah! tu ney jo mujh se wada kya mujhey ata farma. aey Allah! agar ahale- Islam ki ye jamat halaak ho gaee to zamin main teri bandagi nahi hogi. aap qibla ru ho kar apne hathon ko phailaey musalsal apne rab ko pukaartey rahe yahan tak ke aap ki chadar aap ke kandhon se gir gaee. is par Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aap ke paas aaey, chadar uthai aur usey aap ke kandhon par daala, phir peechhey se aap ke sath chimat gaey aur kehney lagey : Allah ke Nabi! apne rab se aap ka maangna aur pukaarna kafi ho gaya. wo jald hi aap se kya hua apna wada pura farmaeyga . is par izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne ye aayat nazil farmai : jab tum log apne rab se madad maang rahe they, to usne tumhari dua qabool ki ke main aik-doosrey ke peechhey utarney waley aik hazaar farishton se tumhari madad karunga. phir Allah ne farishton ke zariey se aap ki madad farmai. abu-Zameel ne kaha : mujhey Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha is doran mein, us din musalmanon mein se aik shakhs apne samney bhaagtey huey mushrikon mein se aik aadmi ke peechhey daud raha tha ke achcha usne apne uper se koda maarney aur uske uper se ghud sawar ki awaz suni, jo keh raha tha : Hezom! aagey badh. us ne apne samney mushrik ki taraf dekha to wo chit pada hua tha, us ne is par nazar dali to dekha ke uski naak par nishan pada hua tha, kode ki zarb ki tarah uska chehra phata hua tha aur wo poorey ka pura sabz ho chuka tha, wo Ansari aaya aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye baat batai to aap ne farmaya : tum ne sach kaha, ye teesrey aasman se (aai hui) madad thi. unhon ( sahaba ( ne us din 70 aadmi qatl kiye aur 70 qaidi banaey . abu-Zameel ne kaha : Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : jab unhon-ne qaidiyon ko giraftaar kar liya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hazrat Abu-Bakar aur Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : un qaidiyon ke barey mein tumhari raey kya hai? to Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aey Allah ke Nabi ! ye hamarey chacha zaad aur khandan ke betey hain. meri raey hai ke aap unse fidya ley lein, ye kaafiron ke khilaf hamari quwwat ka baais hoga, ho sakta hai ke Allah unko Islam ki raah par chala de. iske baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kaha : ibne-khattaab! tumhari kya raey hai? kaha : maine kaha : nahi, Allah ke rasool! Allah ki qism ! meri raey wo nahi jo Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki hai, balke meri raey ye hai ke aap hamein ikhtiyar dein aur ham unki gardanein uda dein. aap Aqeel par Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko ikhtiyar dein wo uski gardan uda dein aur mujhey fulaan. padhi. umr ke ham nasb . padhi. par ikhtiyar dein to main uski gardan uda dun. ye log kufr ke peshwa aur badey sardaar hain. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is baat ko pasand kya jo Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kahi thi aur jo maine kaha tha usey pasand na farmaya, jab agla din hua (aur ( mein hazir hua to dekha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) donon baithey huey hain aur donon ro rahe hain. maine kaha : Allah ke rasool! mujhey bataiye , aap aur aap ka sathi kis cheez par ro rahe hain? agar mujhey rona aaya to main bhi ro-unga aur agar mujhey rona na aaya to bhi main aap donon ke roney ki bina par roney ki koshish karunga. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : main is baat par ro raha hun jo tumharey sathiyon ne unse fidya leney ke barey mein mere samney pesh ki thi, unka azab mujhey us darakht se bhi qareeb tar dikhaya gaya. padhi. wo darakht jo Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke qareeb tha. padhi. aur izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne ye aayatein nazil farmai hain : kisi Nabi ke liye (rawaa) na tha ke uske paas qaidi hon, yahan tak ke wo zamin main achi tarah khoon bahaaey. is farman tak. padhi. to tum usmein se khaao jo halal aur pakeeza ghaneematein tum ne hasil ki hain. to is tarah Allah ne unke liye ghaneemat ko halal kar diya."
4589,"Leis ne hamein Saeed bin abi Saeed se hadis bayan ki ke unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Najad ki taraf ghud-sawaron ka aik dasta bheja to wo banu-Hanifa ke aik aadmi ko pakad laaey, jisey Samaama-bin-Assaal kaha jata tha, wo ahale-yamaama ka sardaar tha, unhon-ne usey masjid ke sutunon mein se aik sutoon ke sath baandh diya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (ghar se) nikal kar uske paas aaey aur puchha : Samama ! tumharey paas kya ( khabar ( hai? us ne jawab diya : aey Muhammad ! mere paas achi baat hai, agar aap qatl karengey to aik aisey shakhs ko qatl karengey jiske khoon ka haq maanga jata hai aur agar ehsan karengey to is par ehsan karengey jo shukr karne wala hai. aur agar maal chahtey hain to talab kijiye , aap jo chahtey hain, aapko diya jaeyga Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey (uske haal par) chhod diya yahan tak ke jab agley se baad ka din ( aainda parson ( hua to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha : Samama ! tumharey paas ( kehney ko) kya hai? us ne jawab diya : ( wahi ( jo maine aap se kaha tha, agar ehsan karengey to aik shukr karne waley par ehsan karengey aur agar qatl karengey to aik khoon waley ko qatl karengey aur agar maal chahtey hain to talab kijiye, aap jo chahtey hain aapko wahi diya jaeyga Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey (usi haal mein) chhod diya yahan tak ke jab agla din hua to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha : Samaama! tumharey paas kya hai? us ne jawab diya : mere paas wahi hai jo maine aap se kaha tha : agar ehsan karengey to aik ehsan shanaas par ehsan karengey aur agar qatl karengey to aik aisey shakhs ko qatl karengey jiska khoon zaaye nahi jata, aur agar maal chahtey hain to talab kijiye, aap jo chahtey hain wahi aapko diya jaeyga to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Samama ko aazad kar do. wo masjid ke qareeb khajooron ke aik baagh ki taraf gaya, ghusl kya, phir masjid mein dakhil hua aur kaha : main gawahi deta hun ke Allah ke siwa koi ibadat ke laaiq nahi aur main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) iske bandey aur rasool hain. aey Muhammad ! Allah ki qism ! poori zamin par aap ke chehrey se badh kar koi chehra nahi tha jis se mujhey bughz ho aur ab aap ke chehrey se badh kar koi chehra nahi jo mujhey zyada mahboob ho. Allah ki qasam! aap ke Deen se badh kar koi Deen mujhey zyada na-pasandida nahi tha, ab aap ka Deen sabse badh kar mahboob Deen ho gaya hai. Allah ki qasam! mujhey aap ke Shahar se badh kar koi Shahar bura nahi lagta tha, ab mujhey aap ke Shahar se badh kar koi aur Shahar mahboob nahi. aap ke ghud-sawaron ne mujhey (us waqt) pakda tha jab main Umra karna chahta tha. ab aap kya ( sahi ( samajhtey hain? to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein (eman ki qabooliyat ki) khushkhabri di aur hukm diya ke Umra ada kare. jab wo Makka aaey to kisi kehney waley ne unse kaha : kya be-deen ho gaey ho? to unhon-ne jawab diya : nahi, balke Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Islam mein dakhil ho gaya hun, aur Allah ki qasam! yamaama se gehun ka aik daana bhi tumharey paas nahi pahunchega yahan tak ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uski ijazat de dein."
4590,tarjama wahi hai jo uper guzra . siwaey iske ke usne kaha : ''agar tum mujhey qatl karogey to aik taaqatwar aadmi ko qatl karogey.''
4591,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : aik baar ham masjid mein they ke) achcha ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamarey paas tashrif laey aur farmaya : yahood ki taraf chalo. ham aap ke sath nikley yahan tak ke unke yahaan pahunch gaey, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey huey, buland awaz se unhein pukara aur farmaya : aey yahood ki jamat ! Islam qabool kar lo, salamati paogey unhon-ne kaha : aey abul-Qaasim! aap ne paigham pahuncha diya hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya : main yahi (paigham pahunchaana) chahta hun, Islam qabool kar lo, salamati paogey unhon-ne kaha : aey abul-Qaasim! aap ne paigham pahuncha diya hai. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya : main yahi chahta hun. aap ne unse teesri martaba kaha aur farmaya : jaan lo! ye zamin Allah aur uske rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki hai aur main chahta hun ke tumhen us zamin se jilaa watan kar dun, tum mein se jisey apne maal ke iwaz kuchh miley to wo usey farokht kar de, warna jaan lo ke ye zamin Allah ki aur uske rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki hai."
4592,"ibne-Juraij ne Musa-bin-Aqba se, unhon-ne Naafe se aur unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke banu-Nazeer aur Qureza ke yahood ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se jang ki to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne banu-Nazeer ko jilaa watan kar diya aur Qureza ko theharney diya aur un par ehsan kya, yahan tak ke iske (eik-dedh saal) baad Qureza ne ( jange-Ehzaab mein dushman ka sath diya aur) jang ki to aap ne (unke chuney huey saalis Hazrat Sad-bin-Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ke faisley par) unke ( jangju ( mardon ko qatl kar diya aur unki auratein , bachchey aur amwaal musalmanon mein taqseem kar diye, albatta unmein se kuchh log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath waabasta ho gaey to aap ne unhein aman ata ki aur wo musalman ho gaey aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( khud apne faisley ki ru se) Madina ke tamam yahood ko jilaa watan kya : bani qainuqaa ko , ye Hazrat Abdullaah-bin-Salaam (Raziallahu anhu) ki qaum thi, banu-Haarisa ke yahood ko aur har Yahudi ko jo Madina mein tha."
4593,Hafs-bin-Maisra ne Musa se ye hadis isi sanad ke sath bayan ki aur ibne-Juraij ki hadis zyada lambi aur zyada mukammal hai.
4594,"ibne-Juraij ne hamein khabar di, kaha : mujhey abu-Zubair ne khabar di, unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : mujhey Hazrat umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di ke unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna : main yahood w nasara ko har sura jazeera Arab se nikal doonga yahan tak ke main musalmanon ke siwa kisi aur ko nahi rehney doonga ."
4595,Sufiyan Sory aur Maaqil bin Ubaidullah donon ne abu-Zubair se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
4596,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba , Muhammad-bin-Musanna aur ibne-Bashar ne. padhi. un sab ke alfaz qareeb-qareeb hain. padhi. hamein hadis bayan ki. padhi. Abu-Bakar ne kaha : hamein ghandar ne Shoba se hadis bayan ki aur doosrey donon ne kaha : hamein Muhammad-bin-Jafar ( ghandar ( ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Shoba ne hadis bayan ki. padhi. unhon-ne Sad bin Ibrahim se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine abu-Umama bin Sahal-bin-Haneef (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne kaha : Qureza ke yahood Hazrat Sad-bin-Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ke faisley (ko qabool karne ki shart ( par) qile se) utar aaey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hazrat Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf paigham bheja , wo gadhey par Sawar ho kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaey, jab wo masjid ke qareeb pahunchey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ansar se farmaya : apne sardaar . padhi. ya ( farmaya : ( apne behtreen aadmi . padhi. ke) istiqbaal ke) liye utho . phir farmaya : ye log tumharey faisley (ki shart ( par) qiley se) utrey hain. unhon-ne kaha : unke jangju afraad ko qatl kar diya jaey aur (unki aurton aur) unke bachchon ko qaidi bana liya jaey. kaha : to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum ne Allah ke faisley ke mutabiq faisla kya hai. aur kabhi-kabhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum ne ( asl ( badshah ke faisley ke mutabiq faisla kya hai. ibne- Musanna ne ye bayan nahi kya : aur kabhi-kabhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum ne badshah ke faisley ke mutabiq faisla kya hai."
4597,Abdur-Rehman-bin-Mehdi ne Shoba se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki aur unhon-ne apni hadis mein kaha : to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum ne unke barey mein Allah ke hukm ke mutabiq faisla kya hai. aur aik baar farmaya : tum ne ( haqiqi ( badshah ( Allah (ke faisley ke mutabiq faisla kya hai.
4598,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : khandaq ke din Hazrat Sad (Raziallahu anhu) zakhmi ho gaey, unhein Quraish ke aik aadmi ne, jisey ibne-Arqa kaha jata tha, teer maara. usne unhein bazu ki badi rag mein teer maara . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke liye masjid mein khema lagwaaya, aap qareeb se unki teemaardaari karna chahtey they. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khandaq se wapas huey, aslaha utara aur ghusl kya to (eik insan ki shakl mein) Jibreel (Alaihissalam) aaey, wo apne sar se gardo-ghubaar jhaad rahe they, unhon-ne kaha : aap ne aslaha utaar diya hai? Allah ki qism ! ham ne nahi utara , unki taraf nikaliyie , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha : kahan ? unhon-ne banu-Quraiza ki taraf ishara kya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse jang ki, wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke faisley par utar aaey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke barey mein faisla Hazrat Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ke sipurd kar diya, unhon-ne kaha : main unke barey mein faisla karta hun ke jangju afraad ko qatl kar diya jaey aur ye ke bachchon aur aurton ko qaidi bana liya jaey aur unke amwaal taqseem kar diye jaaein."
4599,Urwa ne kaha : mujhey bataya gaya hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum ne unke barey mein izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ke faisley ke mutabiq faisla kya hai.
4600,"ibne-Numair ne Hisham se hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey mere walid ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se khabar di ke Hazrat Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ne, jab unka zakhm bhar raha tha, (to dua kartey huey) kaha : aey Allah ! to janta hai ke mujhey terey rastey mein, us qaum ke khilaf jihad se badh kar kisi ke khilaf jihad karna mahboob nahi jinhoney terey rasool ko jhutlaaya aur nikala. agar Quraish ki jang ka koi hissey baqi hai to mujhey zinda rakh taake main terey rastey mein unse jihad karun. aey Allah! mera khayal hai ke tu ney hamarey aur unke darmyan ladai khatm kar di hai. agar tu ney hamarey aur unke darmyan ladai waqei khatm kar di hai to us ( zakhm ( ko phaad de aur mujhey usi mein maut ata farma, chunanche unki hansli se khoon bahney laga, logon ko . padhi. aur masjid mein unke sath banu- ghifaar ka khema tha. padhi. us khoon ne hi khaufzada kya jo unki taraf bah raha tha. unhon-ne puchha : aey khemey waalo! ye kya hai jo tumhari taraf se hamari taraf aa raha hai? to wo Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ka zakhm tha jis se musalsal khoon bah raha hai, chunanche wo usi ( kaifiyat ( mein faut ho gaey."
4601,"Abda ne Hisham se isi sanad ke sath isi tarah hadis bayan ki, albatta unhon-ne kaha : usi raat se khoon bahney laga aur musalsal bahtaa raha yahan tak ke wo wafat pa gaey aur unhon-ne hadis mein ye izafa kiya, kaha : yahi waqt hai jab (eik kaafir ( shaair kehta hai : aey Sad ! banu-Muaz ke (gharaaney ke) Sad ! wo kya tha jo banu-Quraiza ne kiya aur (wo kya tha jo ( banu-Nazeer ne kiya? tumhari zindagi ki qism ! banu-Muaz ka Sad , jis subah un logon ne saza bardasht ki, khub sabr karne wala tha. tum ( Aus ke) logon ne apni haddiyaan is tarah chhodein ke unmein kuchh baqi na bacha tha jabke qaum ( banu-khazraj ( ki haandiyaan garm thin, ubal rahi thin ( unhon-ne apne haleef (saathi) banu-nazeer ka sath diya tha.) aik Karim insan abu-Hubaab (munafiqon ke sardar Abdullah-bin-Ubai-ibne-Salool) ne kaha tha : ( bano ( qainuqaa' ! muqeem raho, mat jao . wo log apne Shahar mein bahut wazan rakhtey they ( baa-waqa't they) jis tarah meetaan pahaad ki chattaanein bahut wazan rakhti hain."
4602,"Hazrat Abdullah (bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne, jis roz aap jange-ehzaab se lautey ham mein manaadi karaai ke koi shakhs banu-Quraiza ke siwa kahin aur namaze Zohar ada na kare. kuchh logon ko waqt nikal janey ka khof mehsus hua to unhon-ne banu-Quraiza (pahunchne) se pahley hi Namaz padh li. jabke dusron ne kaha : chahey waqt khatm ho jaey ham wahin Namaz padhengey jahan Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein Namaz padhney ka hukm diya hai. kaha : to aap ne fareeqain (dono pakshon) mein se kisi ko bhi malaamat na ki."
4603,"ibne-Shahab ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : jab muhajireen Makka se Madina aaey to us haalat mein aaey ke unke paas kuchh bhi na tha, jabke Ansar zamin aur jaaydaadon waley they. to Ansar ne unke sath is tarah hisse daari ki ke wo unhein har saal apne amwaal ki paidawar ka aadha hissey dengey aur ye (muhajireen) unhein mehnat aur mashaqqat se be-niyaaz kar dengey. Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki walida , jo Umme-Sulaim kehlaati thin aur Abdullah-bin-Ubai Talha (Raziallahu anhu) jo Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ke maadri bhai they, ki bhi walida thin. Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki) unhi ( walida ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko khajoor ke apne kuchh darakht diye they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wo apni aazad karda kaneez, Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ki walida , umme-aiman (Raziallahu anhu) ko inayat kar diye they. ibne-Shahab ne kaha : mujhey Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne bataya ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ahale khaibar ke khilaf jang se farigh huey aur Madina wapas aaey to muhajireen ne Ansar ko unke wo atiye wapas kar diye jo unhon-ne unhein apne phalon ( kheton, baaghon ( mein se diye they. kaha : to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne meri walida ko unke khajoor ke darakht wapas kar diye aur umme-aiman (Raziallahu anhu) ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unki jagah apne baagh mein se (eik hissey ( ata farma diya. ibne-Shahab ne kaha : Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ki walida umme-aiman (Raziallahu anhu) ke halaat ye hain ke wo (Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke walid giraami) Abdullah-bin-abdul-Muttalib ki kaneez thin. aur wo Habsha se thin, apne walid ki wafat ke baad jab Hazrat aamna ke yahan Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wilaadat baa-khush-naseebi hui to umme-aiman (Raziallahu anhu) aapko god mein uthatin aur aap ki parwarish mein Sharik rahien yahan tak ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) badey ho gaey to aap ne unhein aazad kar diya, phir Zaid-bin-Haarisa (Raziallahu anhu) se unka nikah kara diya, wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat se panch maah baad faut ho gain."
4604,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba , haamid-bin-Umar-bakraawi aur Muhammad-bin-Abdul-Aala Qaisi , sab ne Moatamir se hadis bayan ki. padhi. alfaz ibne-Abi-Sheba ke hain. hamein Moatamir-bin-Sulaiman Taimi ne apne walid ke waastey se Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki ke koi aadmi. padhi. jabke haamid aur Abdul-Aala ne kaha : koi makhsoos aadmi. padhi. apni zamin se khajooron ke kuchh darakht ( fuqaraaey muhajireen ki khabar-geeri ke liye) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye khas kar deta tha. yahan tak ke Qureza aur banu-Nazeer aap ke liye fateh ho gaey to iske baad jo kisi ne aapko diya tha, wo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey wapas karna shuru kar diya. Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : mere ghar walon ne mujh se kaha ke main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hun aur aap se wo sab ya uska kuchh hissey maangon, jo unke ghar walon ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko diya tha. aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wo umme-aiman (Raziallahu anhu) ko de diya tha. main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya to aap ne wo sab ka sab mujhey de diya. is par umme-aiman (Raziallahu anhu) aaein, mere galley mein kapda daala aur kehney lagein : Allah ki qism ! ham wo (darakht) tumhen nahi dengey , jabke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wo hamein de chukey hain. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : umme-aiman ! usey chhod do, itna-itna tumhara hua. wo kehti thin : hargiz nahi, us zaat ki qism jiske siwa koi haqiqi maabood nahi ! aur aap isi tarah farmatey rahe yahan tak ke aap ne usey das guna ya taqriban das guna ata farma diya."
4605,"hamein Sulaiman-bin-Mugheera ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Humaid-bin-Hilal ne Abdullah-bin-mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : khaibar ke din mujhey charbi ka ( bharaa hua) chamdey ka aik thailaa mila. kaha : maine usey apne sath chimtaa liya aur kaha : aaj ke din mein usmein se kisi ko kuchh nahi doonga. kaha : maine mud kar dekha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) muskuraa rahe they."
4606,"Bahaz-bin-Asad ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Shoba ne hadis sunai, kaha : mujhey Humaid-bin-Hilal ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine Hazrat Abdullah-bin-mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye bataatey huey suna : khaibar ke din hamari taraf chamdey ka aik thailaa phainkaa gaya jis mein khana aur charbi thi, mein usey pakadney ke liye jhaptaa. kaha : maine mud kar dekha to (peechhey) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) maujood they. to mujhey aap se bahut haya aai. Abu-Dawud ne Shoba se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki, albatta unhon-ne charbi ka  bharaa hua) thailaa kaha, khaney ka zikr nahi kiya."
4607,"Mamar ne hamein Zohri se khabar di, unhon-ne Ubaidullah-bin-Abdullaah-bin-Utba se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Hazrat Abu-Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein roo-baroo bataya , kaha : ( muaahida suleh ki) us muddat ke doran mein jo mere aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke darmyan thi, main safar par gaya. kaha : is beech mein, jab main Sham (Syria) mein tha, hiraqal yani Rome ke badshah ke paas Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf se aik khat laya gaya. kaha : usey Dahiya Kalbi (Raziallahu anhu) lekar aaey aur hakime Busraa ke hawale kiya, Busra ke Hakim ne wo Hiraql tak pahuncha diya to Hiraql ne kaha : kya us shakhs ki qaum mein se, jo dawa karta hai ke wo Nabi hai, koi shakhs yahan maujood hai? unhon-ne kaha : haan. kaha : to Quraish ke kuchh afraad samet mujhey bulaya gaya. ham Hiraql ke paas aaey to usne hamein apne samney bithaya aur puchha : tum mein se nasb mein us aadmi ke sabse zyada qareeb kon hai jo dawa karta hai ke wo Nabi hai? Abu-Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine jawab diya : main hun. to un logon ne mujhey unke samney bitha diya aur mere sathiyon ko mere peechhey bitha diya. phir us ne apne tarjuman ko bulaya aur us se kaha : unse keh do : main is aadmi se us shakhs ke barey mein poochhney laga hun jo dawa karta hai ke wo Nabi hai. agar ye mere samney jhoot boley to tum log uska inkar kar dena. kaha : Abu-Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Allah ki qism ! agar ye dar na hota ke meri taraf jhoot ki nisbat ki jaeygi to main jhoot boltaa. phir us ne apne tarjuman se kaha is se poochho : tum mein uska hasab ( khandan ( kaisa hai? kaha : maine jawab diya : wo ham mein hasab wala hai. us ne puchha : kya uske baap-dada aur ijdaad mein se koi badshah bhi tha? maine jawab diya : nahi. us ne puchha : kya usne ( nabwooat ke hawale se) jo kaha, uske kehney se pahley tum is par jhoot bolney ka ilzam lagaatey they? maine jawab diya : nahi. us ne puchha : iske perokar kon log hain? badey log hain ya kamzor log hain? maine jawab diya : balke kamzor log hain. us ne puchha : kya wo badh rahe hain ya kam ho rahe hain? kaha : maine jawab diya : nahi, balke wo badh rahe hain. us ne puchha : kya unmein se koi uske Deen mein dakhil honey ke baad usey na-pasand kartey huey murtad bhi hota hai? maine jawab diya : nahi. us ne puchha : kya tum ne us se jang bhi ki hai? maine jawab diya : haan. us ne puchha : to tumhari us se jang kaisi rahi ? maine jawab diya : hamarey aur uske darmyan jang kuwein ke dol ki tarah hai, wo hamein nuqsan pahunchata hai aur ham usey nuqsan pahunchaatey hain. us ne puchha : kya wo bad-ahdi karta hai? maine jawab diya : nahi, ham uski taraf se (ki gai) suleh ke zamaney mein hain, hamein malum nahi, wo usmein kya karega? kaha : Allah ki qism ! us aik kalimey ke siwa usmein koi aur baat milana mere liye mumkin na hua. us ne puchha : kya us se pahley kisi ne wo baat kahi hai? maine jawab diya : nahi. us ne apne tarjuman se kaha : unse kaho : maine tum se uske hasab ke barey mein puchha to tum ne kaha ke wo tum mein (oonchey) hasab wala hai. rasool isi tarah hotey hain, apni qaum ke aalaa khandanon mein bhejey jatey hain. aur maine puchha : kya iske baap-dada aur ijdaad mein koi badshah tha? to tum ne dawa kiya : nahi, maine (dil mein) kaha : agar iske baap-dada aur ijdaad mein koi badshah hota to main kehta : wo aadmi apne baap-dada ki badhshahat hasil karna chahta hai aur maine tum se iske pairokaaron ke barey mein puchha : wo kamzor log hain ya ashraaf hain? to tum ne kaha : balke wo kamzor log hain, rasulon ke perokar wahi log hotey hain. aur maine tum se puchha ke jo wo kehta hai us se pahley tum is par jhoot ka ilzam lagaatey they, to tum ne kaha : nahi, is tarah mein jaan gaya ke ye mumkin nahi ke wo logon par to jhoot na boley magar Allah par jhoot baandhney lagey aur maine tum se puchha : kya iske Deen mein dakhil honey ke baad koi us se naraz ho kar uske Deen se nikla hai? to tum ne kaha : nahi, eman jab dilon mein rach bas jata hai to isi tarah hota hai. aur maine tum se puchha : kya wo badh rahe hain ya kam ho rahe hain? to tum ne kaha ke wo badh rahe hain, eman aisa hi hota hai yahan tak ke wo mukammal ho jata hai. aur maine tum se puchha : kya tum ne us se ladai ki? to tum ne kaha ke) haan ( tum ne us se ladai ki hai aur tumharey aur uske darmyan jang dol ki tarah hai, wo tum mein se logon ko qatl karta hai aur tum uske logon mein se qatl kartey ho, rasool isi tarah hotey hain, unhein aazmaya jata hai, phir anjam unhi ke haq mein hota hai. aur maine tum se puchha : kya wo ahad shikani karta hai? to tum ne kaha ke wo ahad shikani nahi karta aur rasool isi tarah hotey hain, wo bad-ahdi nahi kartey aur maine tum se puchha : kya us se pahley kisi ne ye baat kahi (ke wo Allah ka rasool hai?) to tum ne kaha : nahi, maine (dil mein) kaha : agar kisi ne us se pahley ye baat kahi hoti to main kehta : ye aadmi wahi baat kehna chahta hai jo us se pahley kahi ja chuki hai. kaha : phir us ne puchha : wo tumhen kis cheez ka hukm deta hai? maine jawab diya : wo hamein Namaz , zakat , sila rehmi aur paakbaazi ka hukm deta hai. usne kaha : agar tum jo uske barey mein kehtey ho, sach hai, to bila shubah wo Nabi hai aur main janta tha ke uska zuhoor (zahir) honey wala hai lekin main ye nahi samajhta tha ke wo tum mein se hoga, aur agar mujhey ilm ho jaey ke main un tak pahunch sakta hun to main unse milney ko mahboob rakhoon aur agar main unke paas hota to main unke paon dhota aur unki hukumat is zamin tak pahunch kar rahegi jo mere qadmon ke nichey hai. kaha : phir us ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka khat mangwaya aur usey padha to usmein ( likha ( tha : Allah ke naam se jo bahut zyada raham karne waalaa, hamesha meherbani karne wala hai, Allah ke rasool Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf se Rome ke badshah Hiraql ke naam , is par salamati ho jisne hidayat ki ittaba (pairvi) ki, iske ba'd, main tumhen Islam ke bulaawey ke sath dawat deta hun, Islam qabool kar lo, salamati pa logey , Islam qabool kar lo, Allah tumhen do baar ajr dega aur agar tum ne munh mod liya to aam logon ka gunah (jo tumharey peechhey chaltey hain) tum par hoga aur aey ahle-kitab ! is baat ki taraf aao jo hamarey aur tumharey darmyan aik jaisi hai ke ham Allah ke siwa kisi ki ibadat na karein, uske sath kisi cheez ko Sharik na karein, ham mein se koi kisi ko Allah ke siwa rab na banaey , phir agar wo munh mod lein to keh dein, (tum ( gawah raho ke ham farman bardaar (Islam qabool karne waale) hain. jab wo khat padhney se farigh hua to uske paas aawaazein buland honey lagein aur shor badh gaya, us ne hamarey barey mein hukm diya to hamein bahar bhej diya gaya. kaha : jab ham bahar nikley to maine apne sathiyon se kaha : abu-Kabsha ke betey ka mamla to bahut bada ho gaya hai, is se to banu-asfar ( ahale Rome (mojooda Itly) (ka badshah bhi khof khata hai. kaha : iske baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke mamley mein mujhey hamesha yaqin raha ke wo ghalib aaeingey , yahan tak ke Allah ne mujh mein uper se ( ghalib karke ( Islam dakhil kar diya."
4608,"Saleh ne ibne-Shahab se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki aur hadis mein ye izafa kiya : jab Allah ne qaisar (ke sar par se) Faaris ke lashkaron ko hata diya to wo us nemat ka shukr ada karne ke liye, jo Allah ne is par ki thi, paidal chal kar teiswin se iliyaa gaya, aur unhon-ne hadis mein) yun ( kaha : Allah ke bandey aur uske rasool Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf se. aur unhon-ne (''اریسین'' areeseen ke bajaey ya ke saath) ''یریسین'' aur Islam ki taraf bulaney waley kalimey ke sath ( daawat deta hun (ke alfaz kahey ."
4609,"Abdul-Aala ne hamein Saeed (bin-abi-Aruba ( se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Qatada se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Kisraa , qaisar , Najashi aur har mutakabbir badshah ko Allah Taala ki taraf bulatey huey khutoot likh bhejey , aur us se wo Najashi murad nahi jiski Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne namaaze-janaaza padhai. (uske baad waley Najashi ki taraf khat likha.)"
4610,"abdul-wahaab-bin-Ata ne Saeed se, unhon-ne Qatada se riwayat ki, kaha : hamein Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki, aur unhon-ne ye nahi kaha : aur ye Najashi wo nahi tha jiski Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne namaaze-janaaza padhai thi."
4611,"Khalid-bin-Qais ne Qatada se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki aur unhon-ne bhi ye zikr nahi kiya : ye Najashi wo nahi tha jiski Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne namaaze-janaaza padhai thi."
4612,"Yunus ne mujhey ibne-Shahab se khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey kaseer-bin-Abbas-bin-abdul-Muttalib (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Hunain ke din main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath maujood tha, main aur Abu-Sufiyan-bin-Haaris-bin-abdul-Muttalib (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath rahe, aap se juda na huey, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne safaid khachchar par) sawar ( they jo farwa-bin-nufasa juzaami ne aapko tohfey mein diya tha. jab musalmanon aur kuffaar ka aamna saamna hua to musalman peeth pher kar bhaagey, ( magar ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne khachchar ko eirh laga kar, kuffaar ki taraf badhney lagey. Hazrat Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke khachchar ki lagaam thaamey huey tha. main chahta tha ke wo tezi se ( aagey ( na badhey aur Abu-Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki rikaab ko pakda hua tha. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Abbas ! keekar ke darakht (ke nichey bait karne) walon ko awaz do. Hazrat Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : . padhi. aur wo buland awaz waley they. maine apni buland tareen awaz se pukar kar kaha : keekar ke darakht waley kahan hain? kaha : Allah ki qism ! meri awaz sun kar unka palatna is tarah tha jaisey gaaey apne bachchon ki) awaz sun kar unki ( taraf palat'ti hai. aur wo ( jawab mein) kehney lagey : hazir hain ! hazir hain ! kaha : to wo kuffaar se bhid gaey, phir Ansar mein bulaawaa diya gaya ( bulaawaa dene waale) kehtey they : aey Ansar ki jamat ! aey Ansar ki jamat ! phir us nidaa ko bani-Haaris-bin-khazraj tak mehdud kar diya gaya aur unhon-ne kaha : aey banu-Haaris-bin-khazraj ! aey banu-Haaris-bin-khazraj ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne khachchar par baithey huey, gardan ko aagey karke dekhney waley ki tarah , unki ladai ka jaaiza liya, us waqt Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ye ghadi hai ke) ladai ka ( tannoor garm hua hai. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kankariyaan pakdein aur unhein kaafiron ke chehron par maara, phir farmaya : Muhammad ke parwardigar ki qism ! wo shikast kha gaey. kaha : main dekhney laga to mere khayal ke mutabiq ladai isi tarah jari thi. kaha : Allah ki qism ! phir yahi hua ke jun-hi aap ne unki taraf kankariyaan phenki to main dekh raha tha ke unki dhaar kund ho gaee hai aur unka mamla peechhey janey ka hai."
4613,"Mamar ne hamein Zohri se isi sanad ke sath isi tarah khabar di, albatta unhon-ne farwa-bin (nufasa ki jagah) Naama juzaami (sahi nufasa hi hai) kaha aur kaha : Kaba ke rab ki qism ! wo shikast kha gaey. Kaba ke rab ki qism ! wo shikast kha gaey aur unhon-ne hadis mein ye izafa kiya : yahan tak ke Allah ne unhein shikast de di. kaha : aisey lagta hai ke main ( ab bhi) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekh raha hun ke aap unke peechhey apne khachchar ko eirh laga rahe hain."
4614,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne hamein Zohri se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey kaseer-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne apne walid se khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : Hunain ke din main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath maujood tha. padhi. aur) aagey baqi bachi ( hadis bayan ki, albatta Yunus aur Mamar ki hadis un ( Sufiyan ( ki hadis se zyada lambi aur zyada mukammal hai."
4615,"abu-Khaisma ne hamein Abu-Ishaq se khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : aik aadmi ne Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : abu-Amaara ! kya aap log Hunain ke din bhaagey they? unhon-ne kaha : nahi, Allah ki qism ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne rukh tak nahi phera , albatta aap ke sathiyon mein se chand naujawaan aur jald baaz ( jang ke liye) nihattey nikley they jin (ke jism ( par aslaha ya bada aslaha nahi tha, to unki mudbhed aisi teer andaz qaum se hui jinka koi teer ( zamin ( par na girtaa tha, ( nishaaney par lagta tha) wo banu-Hawazin aur banu-nazar ke jatthey they. unhon-ne un ( naujawaanon ( ko is tarah se teeron se chhednaa shuru kiya ke koi nishana khata na jata tha. phir wo log wahan se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf badhey , aap apne safaid khachchar par they aur Abu-Sufiyan-bin-Haaris-bin-abdul-Muttalib (Raziallahu anhu) usey chala rahe they, aap nichey utrey ( Allah se) madad mangi aur farmaya : main Nabi hun, ye jhoot nahi mein abdul-Muttalib ka betaa hun. phir aap ne ( naey sirey se) unki saf bandi ki. (aur paansa palat gaya.)"
4616,"Zakariya ne Abu-Ishaq se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : aik aadmi Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaya aur puchha : abu-Amaara ! kya aap log Hunain ke din peeth pher gaey they? to unhon-ne kaha : main Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke barey mein gawahi deta hun ke aap ne rukh tak nahi phera, kuchh jald baaz log aur nihattey Hawazin ke us qabeeley ki taraf badhey , wo teer-andaz log they, unhon-ne un ( naujawaanon ( par is tarah yakbaargi ikatthey teer phainkey jaisey wo tiddi dal hon. is par wo bikhar gaey, aur wo ( Hawazin ke) log Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf badhey , Abu-Sufiyan (bin-Haaris ( (Raziallahu anhu) aap ke khachchar ko pakad kar chala rahe they, to aap nichey utrey , dua ki aur) Allah se) madad mangi , aap farma rahe they : main Nabi hun, ye jhoot nahi, mein abdul-Muttalib ka betaa hun. aey Allah ! apni madad nazil farmaa. Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Allah ki qism ! jab ladai shiddat ikhtiyar kar jati to ham aap ki ot letey they aur ham mein se bahaadur wo hota jo aap ke  yani Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath qadam mila kar khada hota."
4617,"Shoba ne hamein Abu-Is'haq se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine (us waqt) Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) se suna jab ( qabila ( Qais ke aik aadmi ne unse puchha : kya aap log Hunain ke din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko chhod kar bhaagey they? to Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : lekin Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) nahi bhaagey they, us zamaney mein Hawazin ke log ( maahir ( teer andaz they, jab ham ne un par hamla kiya to wo bikhar gaey, phir ham ghaneematon ki taraf mutwajjeh ho gaey to wo teeron ke sath hamarey samney aa gaey. maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko apne safaid khachchar par dekha, Abu-Sufiyan-bin-Haaris (Raziallahu anhu) uski baag thaamey huey they aur aap farma rahe they : main Nabi hun, ye jhoot nahi,main abdul-Muttalib ka betaa hun."
4618,"Sufiyan se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Abu-Ishaq ne Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, kaha : aik aadmi ne unse puchha : abu-Amaara ! . padhi. aur) aagey ( hadis bayan ki, unki hadis un sab ( abu-Khaisma , Zakariya aur Shoba ( ki hadis se ( tafseelaat mein) kam hai aur un sab ki hadis zyada mukammal hai."
4619,"Hazrat Salma-bin-Akwa (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Hunain ki jang ladi, jab hamara dushman se samna hua to main aagey badha phir main aik ghaati par chadh jata hun, mere samney dushman ka aadmi aaya to main is par teer phainktaa hun, wo mujh se chhup gaya. iske baad mujhey malum nahi us ne kya kiya? maine (un ( logon ka jaaiza liya to dekha wo aik dusri ghaati ki taraf zahir huey, unka aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sathiyon ka takraao hua to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sathi peechhey hat gaey aur main bhi shikast khay hue laut'taa hun. mujh (mere jism) par do chaadrein thin, unmein se aik ka maine tehband baandha hua tha aur dusri ko odh rakha tha to mera tehband khul gaya. maine un donon ko ikattha kiya aur shikast khai hui haalat mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas se guzra , aap apne safaid khachchar par they. (mujhey dekh kar) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Akwaa ka betaa ghabraa ke lot aaya hai. jab wo har taraf se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par hamla aawar huey to aap khachchar se nichey utrey. zamin se mitti ki aik muththi li, phir usey samney ki taraf se unke chehron par phainkaa aur farmaya : chehrey bigad gaey. Allah ne unmein se kisi insan ko paida nahi kiya tha magar us aik muththii se unki aankhen bhar dein, so wo peeth pher kar bhag nikley, Allah ne usi (eik muththi khaak ( se unhein shikast di aur) baad iske ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke amwaale ghaneemat musalmanon mein taqseem kiye."
4620,"Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Amr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ahale Taaif ka muhaasra kiya aur unmein se kisi ki jaan na ley sakey to aap ne farmaya : inshaAllah ham kal lot jaengey. aap ke sahaba ne kaha : ham lot jayen jabke ham ne isey fateh nahi kiya? to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya : subah jang ke liye niklo . wo subah nikley to unhein zakhm lagey. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya : ham kal wapas lot jaengey. kaha : to unhein ye baat achi lagi , is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hans padey ."
4621,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko jab Abu-Sufiyan ki aamad ki khabar mili to aap ne mashwara kiya, kaha : Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne guftgu ki to aap ne unse ea'raaz farmaya, phir Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne guftgu ki to aap ne unse ea'raaz farmaya, is par Hazrat Sad-bin-Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) khadey huey aur kehney lagey : aey Allah ke rasool! kya aap ham se ( mashwara karna ( chahtey hain? us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai ! agar aap hamein (apne ghodey ( samandar mein daal dene ka hukm dein to ham unhein daal dengey aur agar aap ham ko unhein zamin ke aakhiri koney tak daudaaney ka hukm dein to ham yahi karengey. kaha : to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne logon ko bulaya , aur wo chal padey yahan tak ke badr mein padao dala. unke paas Quraish ke pani laney waley oont aaey, unmein banu-Hujjaj ka aik siyah faam ghulam bhi tha to unhon-ne usey pakad liya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sathi us se Abu-Sufiyan aur uske sathiyon ke barey mein poochh gachh karne lagey to wo kehney laga : mujhey Abu-Sufiyan ka to pata nahi hai, albatta abu-Jahal , Utba , Sheba , aur Umayya-bin-Khalaf yahan ( qareeb maujood ( hain. jab us ne ye kaha, wo usey maarney lagey. to usne kaha : haan , tumhen batataa hun, Abu-Sufiyan idhar hai. jab unhon-ne usey chhoda aur) dobara ( poochha, to usne kaha : Abu-Sufiyan ka to mujhey ilm nahi hai, albatta abu-Jahal , Utba , Sheba , aur Umayya-bin-Khalaf yahan logon mein maujood hain. jab us ne ye (pahley wali) baat ki to wo usey maarney lagey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey Namaz padh rahe they, aap ne jab ye surate haal dekhi to aap (salam pher kar) paltey aur farmaya is zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai ! jab wo sach kehta hai to tum usey maartey ho aur jab wo tum se jhoot boltaa hai to usey chhod detey ho. kaha : aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ye falan ke marney ki jagah hai. aap zamin par apna hath rakhtey they (aur farmatey they) yahan aur yahan . kaha : unmein se koi bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hath ki jagah se ( zarra barabar bhi) idhar-udhar nahi hua."
4622,"Sheban-bin-Farukh ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Sulaiman-bin Mughira ne hadis sunai, kaha : hamein Sabit Bunani ne Abdullah-bin-ribaah se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : kai wafad Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaey, ye Ramazan ka mahina tha. ( Abdullah-bin-ribaah ne kaha : ( ham aik doosrey ke liye khana taiyaar kartey to Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) jo hamein aksar apni qiyam gaah par bulatey they. aik (din) maine kaha : main bhi kyon na khana taiyaar karun aur sab ko apni qiyam gaah par bulaaun? maine khana banaaney ka keh diya, phir Sham ko Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se mila aur kaha : aaj ki raat mere yahan dawat hai. Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : tu ney mujh se pahley keh diya. (yani aaj main dawat karne wala tha) maine kaha : haan , phir maine un sab ko bulaya. Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aey Ansar ki jamat ! kya main tumhen tumharey mutaalliq hadison mein se aik hadis na bataaoon? phir unhon-ne Makka ke fateh honey ka zikr kiya. iske baad kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey yahan tak ke Makka mein dakhil ho gaey, phir do mein se aik bazu par Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ko bheja aur doosrey bazu par Khalid-bin-Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) ko , abu-Ubaida (bin-jarraah ( (Raziallahu anhu) ko un logon ka sardaar banaya jinke paas zirahein na thin. unhon-ne ghaati ke darmyan wala rasta ikhtiyar kiya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik dastey mein they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey dekha to farmaya : Abu-Hurera ! maine kaha : hazir hun, Allah ke rasool ! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mere sath Ansari ke siwa koi na aaey. Sheban ke ilawa doosrey rawiyon ne izafa kiya : aap ne farmaya : mere liye Ansar ko awaz do. Ansar aap ke ird-gird aagey aur Quraish ne bhi apne obaash logon aur taabe-daaron ko ikattha kiya aur kaha : ham unko aagey kartey hain, agar koi cheez ( kamiyabi ( mili to ham bhi unke sath hain aur agar un par aafat aai to ham se jo maanga jaeyga de dengey. (diyat , jurmaana wghaira.) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum Quraish ke obaashon aur taabe-daaron (har kaam mein pairwi karne walon) ko dekh rahe ho? phir aap ne donon hathon se aik hath ko doosrey hath par (maartey huey) ishara farmaya : (unka safaayaa kar do, unka fitna daba do), phir farmaya : yahan tak ke tum mujh se Safa par aa milo. Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : phir ham chaley, ham mein se jo koi ( kaafiron mein se) jis kisi ko maarna chahta, mar daalta aur koi hamari taraf kisi cheez ( hathiyar ( ko aagey tak na karta, yahan tak ke Abu-Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu) aaey aur kehney lagey : Allah ke rasool ! Quraish ki jamat (ke khoon ( jayez kar diye gaey aur aaj ke baad Quraish na rahe. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( apna pichhla bayan dohraatey huey) farmaya : jo shakhs Abu-Sufiyan ke ghar ke andar chala jaey usko amn hai. Ansar aik doosrey se kehney lagey : unko (yani Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko) apne watan ki muhabbat aur apne kunbey walon par shafqat aa gaee hai. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aur ''wahi'' aaney lagi aur jab ''wahi'' aaney lagti thi to ham se chhipi na rehti . jab ''wahi'' aati to ''wahi'' (ka nuzool ( khatm honey tak koi shakhs Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf apni aankh na uthata tha, gharaz jab ''wahi'' khatm hui to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aey Ansar ke logo ! unhon-ne kaha : Allah ke rasool ! ham hazir hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum ne ye kaha : is shakhs (ke dil mein) apne gaaun ki muhabbat aa gaee hai. unhon-ne kaha : yaqinan aisa to hua tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : hargiz nahi, main Allah ka banda aur uska rasool hun. maine Allah Taala ki taraf hijrat ki aur tumhari taraf ( aaya ( ab meri zindagi bhi tumhari zindagi (ke saath) hai aur maut bhi tumharey sath hai. ye sun kar Ansar rotey huey aagey badhey , wo keh rahe they : Allah Taala ki qism ! ham ne kaha jo kaha mahz Allah Taala aur uske rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath shadeed chaahat (aur unke sath se mahroomi ke khof) ki wjah se kaha tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : be-shak Allah aur uska rasool tumhari tasdeeq kartey hain aur tumhara uzr qabool kartey hain. phir log Abu-Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghar ki taraf aagey aur logon ne apne darwazey band kar liye aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hajre-aswad ke paas tashrif ley aaey aur usko choomaa , phir Baitullah ka tawaaf kiya, phir aap Baitullah ke pahlu mein aik but ke paas aaey, log uski puja kiya kartey they, us waqt Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hath mein kamaan thi, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usko aik taraf se pakda hua tha, jab aap but ke paas aaey to uski aankh mein chubhoney lagey aur farmaney lagey : haq aa gaya aur baatil mit gaya. jab apne tawaaf se farigh huey to Safa pahadi par aaey, is par chadhey yahan tak ke Baitullah ki taraf nazar uthai aur apne donon hath uthaey , phir Allah Taala ki hamd karne lagey aur Allah se jo maangna chaha wo maangney lagey."
4623,"Behaz ne kaha : Sulaiman-bin-Mugheera ne hamein isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne hadis mein (ye ( izafa kiya : aap ne donon hathon se, aik ko doosrey ke sath phertey huey ishara kiya : unko isi tarah kaat dalo jis tarah fasl kaati jati hai unhon-ne hadis mein (ye bhi) kaha : un logon ne kaha : Allah ke rasool ! ham ne ye kaha tha. aap ne farmaya : to phir mera naam kya hoga? hargiz nahi, mein Allah ka banda aur uska rasool hun."
4624,"hamein Hammaad-bin-Salma ne hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( hamein Sabit ne Abdullah-bin-ribaah se khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : ham bataur wafad Hazrat Muawiya-bin-abi-Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaey, aur ham logon mein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bhi they, ham mein se har aadmi aik din apne sathiyon ke liye khana banata , aik din meri baari thi, maine kaha : Abu-Hurera ! aaj meri baari hai, wo sab mere thikaaney par aaey aur abhi khana nahi aaya tha. maine kaha : Abu-Hurera ! kaash! ! aap hamein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se koi hadis sunaien yahan tak ke khana aa jaey. unhon-ne kaha : ham fateh Makka ke din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Khalid-bin-Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) ko daain bazu ( memna ( par) ameer ( muqarrar kiya aur Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ko baain bazu ( Maisra ( par aur abu-Ubaida (Raziallahu anhu) ko piyaadon par aur wadi ke andar (ke rastey ( par tainaat kiya, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Abu-Hurera ! Ansar ko bulao . maine unko bulaya , wo daurhtey huey aaey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Ansar ke logo ! kya tum Quraish ke obaashon ko dekh rahe ho? unhon-ne kaha : ji haan. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : dekho ! kal jab tumhara unse saamnaa ho to unko is tarah kaat dena jis tarah fasl kaati jati hai aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne posheeda rakhtey huey hath se ishara karke bataya aur daahinaa hath baain hath par rakha aur farmaya : ab tum se mulaqat ka wada kooh (pahadi) Safa par hai. Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : to us roz jis kisi ne sar uthaya , unhon-ne usko silaa diya, (yani mar dala. ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Safa pahaad par chadhey , Ansar aaey, unhon-ne Safa ko gher liya, itney mein Abu-Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu) aaey aur kehney laga : Allah ke rasool ! Quraish ki jama'iyat mitaa di gaee, aaj se Quraish na rahe. Abu-Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo koi Abu-Sufiyan ke ghar mein chala gaya usko amn hai aur jo hathiyar daal de usko bhi amn hai aur jo apna darwaza band kar ley usko bhi amn hai. Ansar ne kaha : aap par apne azeezon ki mohabbat aur apne Shahar ki mohabbat ghalib aa gaee hai. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par wahi nazil hui. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum logon ne kaha : mujh par kunbey walon ki mohabbat aur apne Shahar ki muhabbat ghalib aa gaee hai, dekho ! phir (is sura mein) mera naam kya hoga? aap ne teen baar farmaya :  main Muhammad Allah Taala ka banda aur uska rasool hun. maine Allah ke liye tumhari taraf hijrat ki, to ab zindagi tumhari zindagi (ke saath) hai aur maut tumhari maut (ke saath) hai. unhon-ne kaha : Allah ki qism ! ham ne ye Allah aur uske rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki shadeed chaahat (aur aap ki maiyat (sath) se mahroomi ke khof (ke ilawa kisi wjah se nahi kaha tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : to Allah aur uska rasool donon tum ko sachcha jantey hain aur tumhara uzr qabool kartey hain."
4625,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba , Amr Naqid aur ibne-abi-Umar ne. padhi. alfaz ibne-Abi-Sheba ke hain. padhi. kaha : hamein Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne ibne-abi-najeeh se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Mujahid se, unhon-ne abu-Ma'mar se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Makka mein dakhil huey to Kaba ke gird teen so sath but they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) har aik ko apne hath mein pakdi hui lakdi se kachokaa de kar giraaney lagey aur ye farmaney lagey : haq aa gaya aur baatil mit gaya, bila shubah baatil mitney wala hai. haq aa gaya aur baatil na shuruat karta hai aur na lautaataa hai) balke donon izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah jalaala ke kaam hain. ( ibne-abi-Umar ne izafa kiya : fateh Makka ke din ."
4626,"Sory ne ibne-abi-najeeh se isi sanad ke sath pehli aayat ke aakhir tak riwayat ki, dusri aayat bayan nahi ki aur . padhi. (nasban) ke bajaey (sanmaa) kaha : (donon ke mana but ke hain.)"
4627,"Ali-bin-Mus'hir aur Wakee ne Zakariya se, unhon-ne Shabi se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Abdullah-bin-mutee' ne apne bap ( mutee'-bin- Aswad (Raziallahu anhu)) se khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : jis din Makka fateh hua maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko kehtey huey suna : aaj ke baad qiyamat tak koi qureshi baandh kar qatl na kiya jaey."
4628,"Abdullah-bin-Numair ne kaha : hamein Zakariya ne isi sanad ke sath yahi hadis sunai aur ye izafa kiya, kaha is din Quraish ke Aas ( naafarmaan ( naam ke logon mein se, mutee' ke siwa , koi musalman nahi hua. uska naam aasi tha, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uska naam ( badal kar) mutee' rakh diya."
4629,"Muaz Anbari ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Abu-Ishaq se hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : maine Bara-bin-Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huey suna : Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne us suleh ka muaahida likha jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur mushrikon ke darmyan Hudaibiya ke din hui thi. unhon-ne likha : ye ( muaahida ( hai jis par tahreeri suleh ki Allah ke rasool , Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne. un logon ( mushrikon ( ne kaha : Allah ke rasool mat likhiye , isliye ke agar ham yaqin jantey ke aap Allah ke rasool hain to ham aap se na ladtey . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : is lafz ko mitaa do. unhon-ne kaha : jo is ( lafz ( ko mitaaey ga wo main nahi. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usko apne hath se mitaa diya, kaha : unhon-ne jo shartein rakhein unmein ye bhi thi ke) musalman ( Makka mein aaein aur teen din tak muqeem rahen aur hathiyar lekar Makka mein dakhil na hon, siwaey-iske ke chamdey ke thailey mein hon. ( Shoba ne kaha ( maine Abu-Ishaq se kaha : chamdey ke thailey se kya murad hai? unhon-ne kaha : niyaam aur jo iske andar hai."
4630,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Abu-Ishaq se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Bara-bin-Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, keh rahe they : jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hudaibiya (mein aa kar suleh ki guftgu karne) walon se suleh ki to unke beech Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne tahreer likhi , kaha : unhon-ne Muhammad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) likha , phir Muaz ki hadis ki tarah bayan kiya, magar unhon-ne : ye hai jis par tahreer suleh ki (ka jumla ( bayan nahi kiya."
4631,"Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim Hanzali aur Ahmed bin janab missisi donon ne Esa-bin-Yonus se. lafz Ishaq ke hain. padhi. riwayat ki, kaha : hamein Esa-bin-Yonus ne khabar di, hamein Zakariya ne Abu-Ishaq se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Bara (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko Baitullah ke paas rok liya gaya, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Makka walon ne is baat par suleh ki ke) aainda saal ( Makka mein dakhil hon aur teen din tak usmein rahen aur hathiyar rakhney ke thelon : talwaar aur uske niyaam ke ilawa (koi hathiyar lekar) us Shahar mein dakhil na hon aur kisi Makka waley ko apne sath na ley jayen aur unke sath aaney walon mein se jo wahan reh jaey (mushrikon ka sath qabool kar ley) to usko mana na karein. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : is shart ko hamarey darmyan likho ( بسم الله الرحمن الرحيم ( ye hai jis par aapsi faisla kya Allah Taala ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne. mushrik boley : agar ham ye yaqin jantey ke aap Allah Taala ke rasool hain to aap ki pairwi kartey, balke yun likhiye : Muhammad-bin-Abdullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya un (alfaz ( ko mitaa dein. unhon-ne kaha : Allah ki qism ! main (apne hath se) na mitaunga. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : achchha, mujhey us (jumley) ki jagah dikhao. Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne dikha di, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usko mita diya aur ibne- Abdullah likh diya (jab hasab muaahida agley saal aa kar Umra ada farmaya ( to teen roz hi Makka muazzama mein rahe. jab tesraa din hua to mushrikon ne Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : ye tumharey sahib ki shart ka aakhiri din hai, unse kaho : ab wo chaley jayen, unhon-ne aapko bataya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : achchha aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (Makka se) nikal aaey. ibne-janab ne ham aap ki pairwi kartey ke bajaey ham aap ki bait kartey. kaha."
4632,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Quraish ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se musaalihat ki, unmein Suhail-bin-Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bhi they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : likho : ( بسم الله الرحمن الرحيم ( Suhel kehney lagey : jahan tak bismillah ka talluq hai to ham ( بسم الله الرحمن الرحيم ( ko nahi jaantey, lekin wo likho jisey ham jantey hain : ( باسمك اللهم ( phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : likho : Muhammad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf se. wo log kehney lagey : agar ham yaqin jantey ke aap Allah ke rasool hain to ham aap ki pairwi kartey, lekin apna aur apne walid ka naam likho , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : likho : Muhammad-bin-Abdullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf se. un logon ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par shart lagai ke aap logon mein se jo ( hamarey paas ( aa jaeyga ham usey aap logon ko wapas na karengey aur ham mein se jo aap ke paas aaya aap usey ham ko wapas kar dengey. ( sahaba ne) puchha : aey Allah ke rasool! kya ham ye likh dein ? farmaya : haan , ham mein se jo shakhs unke paas chala gaya to usey Allah ne ham se door kar diya aur unmein se jo hamarey paas aayega Allah uske liye kushadgi aur nikalney ka rasta paida farma dega."
4633,"Habib bin abi Sabit ne abu-Waeil (Shaqeeq) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Sahal-bin-Haneef (Raziallahu anhu) jange-siffin ke roz khadey huey aur) logon ko mukhaatab karke ( kaha : logo ! ( ameerul-momeneen par ilzam lagaaney ke bajaey) khud ko ilzam 2 (Suleh ko mustarad karke Allah aur uske bataaey huey rastey se tum hat rahe ho ( ham Hudaibiya ke din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they aur agar ham jang ( hi ko naaguzeer ( dekhtey to jang kar guzartey. ye us suleh ka waqia hai jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur mushrekeen ke darmyan hui. ( ab to musalmanon ke 2 girohon ka mamla hai.) umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) aaey, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! kya ham haq par aur wo baatil par nahi ? aap ne farmaya : kyon nahi ! kaha : kya hamarey maqtool jannat mein aur unke maqtool aag mein na jaeinge? farmaya : kyon nahi ! kaha : to ham apne Deen mein nichey lag kar (Suleh ( kyon karein ( nichey lag kar kyon suleh karein? (aur is tarah kyon lot jayen ke Allah ne hamarey aur unke darmyan faisla nahi kiya? to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Khattab ke betey ! main Allah ka rasool hun, (uske hukm se suleh kar raha hun) Allah mujhey kabhi zaaye nahi karega. kaha : umr (Raziallahu anhu) ghussey ke aalim mein chal padey aur sabr na kar sakey. wo Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaey aur kaha : aey Abu-Bakar ! kya ham haq par aur wo baatil par nahi ? kaha : kyon nahi ! kaha : kya hamarey maqtool jannat mein aur unke maqtool aag mein nahi? unhon-ne kaha : kyon nahi ! (Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : to ham apne Deen mein nichey lag kar) jaisi suleh wo chahtey hain unhein) kyon dein? aur is tarah kyon lot jayen ke Allah ne hamarey aur unke darmyan faisla nahi kiya? to unhon-ne kaha : ibne-khattaab! wo Allah ke rasool hain, Allah unhein hargiz kabhi zaaye nahi karega. kaha : to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par fateh (ki khushkhabri) ke sath Quran utra. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko bulwaya aur unhein (jo nazil hua tha) wo padhwaaya. unhon-ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! kya ye fateh hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : haan. to (us par) umr (Raziallahu anhu) ka dil khush ho gaya aur wo lot aaey."
4634,"abu-Kuraib Muhammad-bin Alaa aur Muhammad-bin-Abdullah bin Numer donon ne kaha : hamein abu-Muawia ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Shaqiq (bin Salma abu-Waail ( se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine siffin mein Sahal-bin-Haneef (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna : logo! apni raey par) ghalat honey ka ( ilzam lagaao . Allah ki qism ! maine abu-jandal (Raziallahu anhu) (ke waqiey (ke din apne aapko us haalat mein dekha ke agar main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke (Suleh ke) mamley ko radd kar sakta to radd kar deta. Allah ki qism ! ham ne kabhi kisi kaam ke liye apne kandhon par talwaarein nahi rakhin thin magar un talwaaron ne hamarey liye aisey mamley tak pahunchne mein aasani kar di jis ko ham jantey they, siwaey tumharey maujooda mamley ke. ibne-Numair ne kabhi kisi mamley ke liye ke alfaz bayan nahi kiye."
4635,"Jarir aur Wakee donon ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki, un donon ki hadis mein ye alfaz hain : aisey kaam ki taraf jo hamein mushkil mein mubtala kar raha tha."
4636,"abu-Haseen ne abu-Waeil se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine siffin mein Sahal-bin-Haneef (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : apne Deen ke muqaabley main apni raey par ilzam dharo . abu-jandal (Raziallahu anhu) (ke waqiey (ke din maine khud ko is haalat mein dekha ke agar main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke faisley ko radd kar sakta (to haashaa w kalaa radd kar deta .) lekin ye mamla aisa hai ke ham iske aik koney ko mazbut nahi kar patey ke hamarey samney uska doosra kona khul jata hai. (kyonke ye musalmanon ka aapas mein ikhtilaf hai.)"
4637,"Saeed-bin-abi-Aruba ne hamein Qatada se hadis sunai ke Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein hadis sunai, kaha : jab Sura Fateh ki aayat 1 se 5 tak utri (to ye (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki Hudaibiya se waapsi ka mauqa tha aur logon ke dilon mein gham aur dukh ki kaifiyat taari thi, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hudaibiya mein qurbani ke oont nehar kar diye they, to (is mauqe par) aap ne farmaya : mujh par aik aisi aayat nazil ki gaee hai jo mujhey poori duniya se zyada mahboob hai."
4638,"Motamir ke walid ( Sulaiman ( , Hammam aur Sheban sab ne Qatada se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se Saeed-bin-abi-Aruba ki hadis ki tarah riwayat ki."
4639,"Hazrat Huzefa bin Yaman (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke jange-badr mein mere shamil na honey ki wjah sirf ye thi ke main aur mere walid Husail (Raziallahu anhu) (jo Yamaan ke laqab se Maruf they) donon nikley to hamein kuffaare-Quraish ne pakad liya aur kaha : tum Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas jana chahtey ho? ham ne kaha : unke paas jana nahi chahtey, ham to sirf Madina Munawra jana chahtey hain. unhon-ne ham se Allah ke naam par ye ahad aur meesaaq liya ke ham Madina jaeynge lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath mil kar jang nahi karengey, ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar aapko ye khabar di, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum donon lot jao, ham unse kya hua ahad pura karengey aur unke khilaf Allah Taala se madad maangengey."
4640,"Ibrahim Taimi ke walid (Yazeed bin Sharik) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : ham Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas they, aik aadmi ne kaha : agar main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ahade-mubaarak ko pa leta to aap ke sath jihad karta aur khub ladta, Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : kya tum aisa kartey? maine jange-Ehzaab ki raat ham sab ko dekha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they, hamein tez hawa aur sardi ne apni giraft mein ley rakha tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya koi aisa mard hai jo mujhey (is) qaum (ke andar) ki khabar la de? qiyamat ke din Allah Taala usko mere sath rakhey! ham khamosh rahe aur ham mein se kisi ne aapko koi jawab na diya, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phir farmaya : koi shakhs hai jo mere paas un logon ki khabar ley aaey? qiyamat ke din Allah Taala usko mere sath rakhey ! ham khamosh rahe aur ham mein se kisi ne koi jawab na diya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phir farmaya : hai koi shakhs jo un logon ki khabar la de ? qiyamat ke din Allah Taala usko meri rifaaqat ata farmaai ! ham khamosh rahe, ham mein se kisi ne koi jawab na diya, aap ne farmaya : Huzefa ! khadey ho jao aur tum mujhey unki khabar la ke do. jab aap ne mera naam lekar bulaya to maine uthney ke siwa koi chaara na paya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jao un logon ki khabrein mujhey la do aur unhein mere khilaf bhadka na dena. (koi aisi baat ya harkat na karna ke tum pakdey jao, aur wo mere khilaf bhadak uthein ( jab main aap ke paas se gaya to meri haalat ye ho gaee jaisey main Hammam mein chal raha hun, ( pasiney mein nahaya hua tha) yahan tak ke main unke paas pahuncha , maine dekha ke Abu-Sufiyan apni pusht aag se saink raha hai, maine teer ko kamaan ki beech mein rakha aur usko nishana bana dena chaha , phir mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka ye farman yad aa gaya ke unhein mere khilaf bhadka na dena (ke jang aur tez ho jaey) agar main us waqt teer chala deta to wo nishana bin jata, main lota to (mujhey aisey lag raha tha) jaisey main Hammam mein chal raha hun, phir jab main aap ki khidmat mein hazir hua to maine aapko un logon ki (saari) khabar batai aur main farigh hua to mujhey thand lagney lagi, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey (apni us) chaadar ka bacha hua hissey odha diya jo aap (ke jism) par thi, aap usmein Namaz padh rahe they. main ( usko odh kar) subah tak sota raha, jab subah hui to aap ne farmaya : aey khub soney waley ! uth jao."
4641,"Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke jange-Uhud ke din Rasulullah (sl), Ansar ke saat (7) aur Quraish ke 2 aadmiyon ( Sad-bin-abi-Waqas aur Talha bin Ubaidullah Taimi (Raziallahu anhu)) ke sath (lashkar se alag karke) tanha kar diye gaey, jab unhon-ne aapko gher liya to aap ne farmaya : unko ham se kon hataaeyga? uske liye jannat hai, ya (farmaya :) wo jannat mein mera rafeeq hoga. to Ansar mein se aik shakhs aagey badha aur us waqt tak ladta raha, yahan tak ke wo Shahid ho gaya, unhon-ne phir se aapko gher liya, aap ne farmaya : unhein kon ham se door hataaeyga? uske liye jannat hai, ya (farmaya :) wo jannat mein mera rafeeq hoga. phir Ansar mein se aik shakhs aagey badha wo lada yahan tak ke Shahid ho gaya, phir ye silsila yoonhi chalta raha yahan tak ke wo saaton Ansari Shahid ho gaey, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne (un qureshi) sathiyon se farmaya : ham ne apne sathiyon ke sath insaf nahi kya."
4642,"abu-Hazim ke betey Abdul-Azeez ne apne walid se bayan kya ke unhon-ne Hazrat Sahal-bin-Sad (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unse jange-Uhud ke din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zakhmi honey ke mutaalliq sawal kya ja raha tha, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka chehra Mubarak zakhmi ho gaya tha aur samney (sanaaya ke saath) ka aik daant (rubaai) toot gaya tha aur khod sar par tukdey-tukdey ho gaya tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sahibzadi Sayeda Fatima (Raziallahu anha) (aap ke chehrey se) khoon dho rahi thin aur Hazrat Ali-bin abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) dhaal se us ( zakhm ( par pani daal rahe they, jab Sayeda Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ne ye dekha ke pani dalney se khoon nikalney mein izafa ho raha hai to unhon-ne chataai ka aik tukda lekar jalaaya wo raakh ho gaya, phir usko zakhm par laga diya to khoon ruk gaya."
4643,"Yaqoob bin Abdur-Rehman al-Qari ne abu-Hazim se bayan kya ke unhon-ne Hazrat Sahal-bin-Sad (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unse Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zakhm ke mutaalliq sawal kya ja raha tha, unhon-ne kaha : suno ! Allah ki qism ! mujhey achi tarah malum hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka zakhm kon dho raha tha aur pani kon daal raha tha aur aap ke zakhm par kon si dawaai lagai gaee, phir Abdul-Azeez ki hadis ki tarah bayan kya, magar unhon-ne ye izafa kya : aur aap ka chehra anwar zakhmi ho gaya aur. padhi. (khod) tukdey-tukdey ho gaya. padhi. ki jagah toot gaya kaha."
4644,"ibne-Uena, Saeed-bin-abi-Hilal aur Muhammad-bin Mutarrif, un sab ne abu-Hazim se, unhon-ne Hazrat Sahal-bin-Sad (Raziallahu anhu) se yahi hadis Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, ibne-abi Hilal ki hadis mein hai : aap ka chehra Mubarak nishana banaya gaya aur ibne- Mutarrif ki hadis mein hai : aap ka chehra Mubarak zakhmi hua."
4645,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke jange-Uhud ke din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka ( sanaaiya ke sath wala ( rubaai daant toot gaya aur aap ke sar mein zakhm laga, aap apne sar se khoon poonchhtey they aur farmatey they : wo qaum kaisey falaah paaeygi jisne apne Nabi ke sar mein zakhm lagaya aur uska rubaai ka daant tod diya, aur wo unhein Allah ki taraf bula raha tha. is mauqe par Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil farmai is mamley mein aap ke hath mein koi cheez nahi (ke wo Allah unki taraf tawajjoh farmaai ya unko azab de ke wo zaalim hain. ("
4646,"Muhammad-bin-Abdullah bin Numer ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Wakee ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Aamash ne Shaqiq se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Abdullah (bin Masood ( (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : jaisey main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf dekh raha hun, aap anbiya mein se aik Nabi ka waqia bayan farma rahe they jinhein unki qaum ne maara, wo apne chehrey se khoon poonchh rahe they aur (ye) farma rahe they : aey Allah! meri qaum ko maaf kar de, wo nahi jantey (ke wo kya kar rahe hain.)"
4647,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba ne kaha : hamein Wakee aur Muhammad-bin-Bishr ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath riwayat bayan ki, usmein unhon-ne ye kaha : to wo (Nabi (Alaihissalam)) apni peshani se khoon poonchhtey jatey they."
4648,"Hammam-bin-Munabba se riwayat hai, kaha : ye hadisein hain jo hamein Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan kin, unhon-ne kai hadisein bayan kin, unmein se aik ye hai : aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya is qaum par Allah ka ghazab shadeed ho gaya jinhoney Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath ye kya aap us waqt apne rubaai daant ki taraf ishara farma rahe they. aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala us shakhs par sakht ghazab naak hota hai jis ko Allah ka rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Allah ki raah mein (jihad kartey huey) qatl kar de."
4649,"Zakariya (bin abi Zayda ( ne Abu-Ishaq se, unhon-ne Amr-bin-Memoon Awdi se, unhon-ne ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : aik baar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Baitullah ke paas Namaz padh rahe they, abu-Jahal aur uske sathi bhi baithey huey they, aur aik din pahley aik ontni zabah hui thi. abu-Jahal ne kaha : tum mein se kon uth kar bani falan ke mohalley se ontni ki bachchey wali jhilli ( bachche daani) laaeyga aur Muhammad sajdey mein jayen to usko unke kandhon ke darmyan rakh dega ? qaum ka sabse bad-bakht shakhs ( Aqba bin abi Muet) utha aur usko ley aaya. jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sajdey mein gaey to usne wo jhilli aap ke kandhon ke darmyan rakh diya, phir wo aapas mein khub hansey aur aik doosrey par girney lagey. main khada hua dekh raha tha, kash! ! mujhey kuchh bhi tahaffuz hasil hota to main us jhilli ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki pusht se utha kar phenk deta, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sajdey mein they. apna sar Mubarak nahi utha rahe they, yahan tak ke aik shakhs ne ja kar Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ko khabar di, wo aaein, halanke wo us waqt kam umr bachchi thin, unhon-ne wo jhilli utha kar aap se door phenki. phir wo un logon ki taraf mutwajjeh huin aur unhein sakht sust kaha, jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni Namaz mukammal kar li to aap ne bazu buland karke unke khilaf dua ki, aap jab koi dua kartey they, to teen martaba dohraatey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) agar kuchh maangtey to teen baar maangtey they, phir aap ne teen martaba farmaya : aey Allah ! Quraish par giraft farma. jab Quraish ne aap ki awaz suni to unki hansi jati rahi aur wo aap ki baddua se khof-zada ho gaey. aap ne phir baddua farmai : aey Allah ! abu-Jahal bin Hisham par giraft farma aur Utba-bin- Rabee , Sheba bin Rabee , Waleed bin Aqba , Umayya-bin-Khalaf , Aqba bin abi Muet par giraft farma. padhi. ( Abu-Ishaq ne kaha : ( unhon ( Amr-bin-Memoon) ne saatwen shakhs ka naam bhi liya tha lekin wo mujhey yad nahi raha (uske baad Abu-Ishaq ko saatwen shakhs Umara bin Waleed ka naam yad aa gaya tha, sahi al-bukhari, hadis : 520). padhi. ( ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : (us zaat ki qism jisne Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko haq ke sath maboos kya hai ! jinka aap ne naam liya tha maine badr ke din unko maqtool padey dekha, phir un sab ko ghaseet kar kuwein, badr ke kuwein ki taraf ley jaya gaya aur unhein usmein daal diya gaya. Abu-Ishaq ne kaha is hadis mein Waleed bin Aqba (ka naam ( ghalat hai. ( sahi Waleed bin Utba hai.)"
4650,"Shoba ne kaha : maine Abu-Ishaq se suna, wo Amr-bin-Memoon se hadis bayan kar rahe they, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke (eik baar) jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sajdey mein they aur aap ke gird Quraish ke log baithey huey they ke Aqba bin abi Muet aik zabah ki hui ontni ki bachchey wali jhilli lekar aaya aur usko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki pusht par phenk diya, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (sajdey se) sar na uthaya, phir Sayeda Fatima (Raziallahu anha) aain aur us jhilli ko aap ki pusht se uthaya aur jin logon ne ye harkat ki thi unko baddua di, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (unke barey mein) farmaya : aey Allah ! Quraish ke us giroh par giraft farma, abu-Jahal bin Hisham, Utba-bin- Rabee, Sheba bin Rabee, Aqba bin abi Muet aur Umayya-bin-Khalaf ya Ubai-bin-Khalaf. padhi. Shoba ko shak hai, par giraft farma! (Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : maine unko dekha, wo jange-badr ke din qatl kiye gaey aur unko kuwein mein daal diya gaya, albatta Umayya-bin-Khalaf ya Ubai bin Khalaf ke jod jod kat chukey they, usey (ghaseet kar) kuwein mein nahi daala ja saka."
4651,"Sufiyan ne Abu-Ishaq se isi sanad ke sath isi tarah riwayat ki aur is mein ye izafa kya ke aap teen baar ( dua karna ( pasand farmatey they, aur aap ne teen baar farmaya : aey Allah ! Quraish par giraft farma, aey Allah ! Quraish par giraft farma, aey Allah ! Quraish par giraft farma aur is mein Waleed bin Utba aur Umayya-bin-Khalaf ka naam liya (Ubai bin Khalaf aur Umayya-bin-Khalaf ke naamon mein) shak nahi kya, Abu-Ishaq ne kaha : saatwan shakhs main bhool gaya."
4652,"Zuhair ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Abu-Ishaq ne Amr-bin-Memoon se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Baitullah ki taraf munh karke Quraish ke chh aadmiyon ke khilaf baddua ki, unmein abu-Jahal , Umayya bhi Khalaf , Utba-bin- Rabee , Sheba bin Rabee aur Aqba bin abi Muet they. main Allah ki qism kha kar kehta hun : maine unko badr (ke maidan) mein aundhey padey huey dekha, dhoop ne un (ke laashon) ko bilkul badal diya tha aur wo aik garm din tha."
4653,"Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ahliya mohtarma Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne hadis bayan ki ke unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! kya aap par koi aisa din bhi aaya jo Uhud ke din se zyada shadeed ho? aap ne farmaya : mujhey tumhari qaum se bahut takleef pahunchi, jab main khud ko ibne-abd ya lail bin abd kalaal ke samney ley gaya (yani usko da'wate-Islam di) lekin jo main chahta tha us ne meri baat na maani, main ghamzada ho kar chal padaa aur Qarn-Saalib par pahunch kar hi meri haalat behtar hui, maine sar uthaya to mujhey aik badal nazar aaya, us ne mujh par saaya kya hua tha, maine dekha to usmein Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) they, unhon-ne mujhey awaz de kar kaha : izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne jo kuchh aap ne apni qaum se kaha wo aur unhon-ne jo aapko jawab diya wo sab sun liya, Allah Taala ne pahadon ka farishta aap ki taraf bheja hai taake aap un kuffaar ke mutaalliq usko jo chaahein hukm dein. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : phir mujhey pahadon ke Farishtey ne awaz di aur salam kya, phir kaha : aey Muhammad ! Allah Taala ne aap ki qaum ki taraf se aapko diya gaya jawab sun liya, main pahadon ka farishta hun aur mujhey aap ke rab ne aap ke paas bheja hai ke aap mujhey jo chaahein hukm dein, agar aap chaahein to main un donon sanglaakh pahadon ko (utha kar) unke uper rakh dun. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se farmaya : balke main ye ummeed karta hun ke Allah Taala unki pushton se aisey log nikalega jo sirf Allah ki ibadat karengey aur uske sath kisi ko Sharik nahi thehraengey."
4654,"abu-Awana ne Aswad bin Qais se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jundub bin Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : un jangon mein se aik mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ungli khoon aalud ho gaee to aap ne farmaya : to aik ungli hi hai jo zakhmi hui aur tu ney jo takleef uthai wo Allah ki raah mein hai."
4655,ibne-Uena ne Aswad bin Qais se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki aur kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik lashkar mein they aur) wahan (aap ki ungli zakhmi ho gaee.
4656,"Sufiyan bin Aswad bin Qais se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna ke aik baar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ki aamad mein taakheer ho gaee, mushrekeen kehney lagey ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko alwadaa keh diya gaya. to izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne ye nazil farmaya : qism hai dhoop chadhtey waqt ki, aur qism hai raat ki jab wo chhaa jaey! (aey Nabi!) aap ke rab ne na aapko rukhsat kya aur na bezaar hua."
4657,"Zuhair ne Aswad bin Qais se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Jundub bin Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bimar ho gaey aur 2 ya teen raatein uth na sakey to aik aurat aap ke paas aai aur kehney lagi : aey Muhammad ! mujhey lagta hai ke aap ke shaitan ne aapko chhod diya hai, maine 2 ya teen raaton se usey aap ke qareeb aatey nahi dekha. kaha : is par Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil farmai : qism hai dhoop chadhtey waqt ki aur raat ki jab wo chhaa jaey ! (aey Nabi ! (aap ke rab ne na aapko rukhsat kya aur na wo bezaar hua."
4658,Shoba aur Sufiyan ( Sory ( ne Aswad bin Qais se isi sanad ke sath un donon ki hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
4659,"Mamar ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Urwa (bin Zuber ( se khabar di ke Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein bataya ke (eik baar) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik gadhey par sawari farmai, is par paalaan tha aur uske nichey fidak ki bani hui aik chadar thi, aap ne Usama (bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu)) ko peechhey bithaya hua tha, aap qabila banu- Haris bin khazraj mein Hazrat Sad-bin-Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) ki iyaadat karna chahtey they. ye jange-badr se pahley ka waqia hai, aap rastey mein aik majlis se guzrey jahan musalman, but-parast aur mushrik aur Yahudi miley juley maujood they, unmein Abdullah-bin Ubai bhi tha aur majlis mein Abdullaah-bin-Rawaaha (Raziallahu anhu) bhi maujood they. jab sawari ki gard majlis ki taraf uthi to Abdullah-bin Ubai ne chadar se apni naak dhanp li aur kehney laga : ham par gard na udaaein. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne un sab ko salam kya, ruk gaey, phir aap sawari se utrey, un logon ko Islam ki dawat di aur un par Quran Majeed ki tilawat ki. Abdullah-bin Ubai ne kaha : aey shakhs! us se achi baat aur koi nahi hogi ke jo kuchh aap keh rahe hain agar wo sach hai to bhi hamari majlison mein aa kar hamein takleef na pahunchaaein aur apne ghar lot jayen aur ham mein se jo shakhs aap ke paas aaey usko sunaein. padhi. Hazrat Abdullaah-bin-Rawaaha (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aap hamari majlis mein tashrif laaein . ham usko pasand kartey hain, phir musalman, yahood aur but parast aik doosrey ko bura bhala kehney lagey, yahan tak ke aik doosrey par toot padney par taiyaar ho gaey. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unko musalsal dheemaa kartey rahe, phir aap apni sawari par baithey, Hazrat Sad-bin-Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaey aur farmaya : Sad ! aap ne nahi suna ke abu-Hubaab ne kya kaha hai? aap ki murad Abdullah-bin Ubai se thi, us ne is-is tarah kaha hai. (hazrat Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : ya Rasulullah ! usko maaf kar dijiye aur us se darguzar kijiye . be-shak Allah Taala ne aapko jo ata kya hai so kya hai. is nashebi nakhlistaani ilaaqey mein basney walon ne mil jul kar ye tay kar liya tha ke usko (badhshahat ka ( taaj pahnaaengey aur uske sar par (riyaasat ka ( amaama baandhengey, phir jab Allah Taala ne, us haq ke zariey jo aapko ata farmaya hai, us ( faisley ( ko radd kar diya to is bina par usko halaq mein phanda lag gaya aur aap ne jo dekha hai us ne usi bina par kya hai. so Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey maaf kar diya."
4660,Aqeel ne ibne-Shahab (Zohri ( se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki aur ye izafa kya : ye Abdullah (bin abi ( ke) zahiri taur par) Islam (ka elaan karne) se pahley ka waqia hai.
4661,"Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha gaya : (kya hi achchha ho ( agar aap (Islam ki dawat dene ke liye) Abdullah-bin Ubai ke paas bhi tashrif ley jayen! Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik gadhey par sawari farma kar uski taraf gaey aur musalman bhi gaey, wo shorili zamin thi, jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uske paas pahunchey to wo kehney laga : mujh se door rahen , Allah ki qasam! aap ke gadhey ki bu se mujhey azeeyat ho rahi hai. Ansar mein se aik shakhs ne kaha : Allah ki qism ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka gadhaa tum se zyada khushbu daar hai. is par Abdullah-bin Ubai ki qaum mein se aik shakhs uski himaayat mein, ghussey mein aa gaya. kaha : donon mein se har aik ke sathi ghussey mein aa gaey. kaha : to unmein hathon , chhadiyon aur jooton ke sath ladai honey lagi, phir hamein ye baat pahunchi ke unhi ke barey mein ye aayat nazil hui : agar musalmanon ki 2 jamatein aapas mein lad padein to un donon ke darmyan suleh karao."
4662,"Ismail ibne-Ulaih ne kaha : hamein Sulaiman Taimi ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : hamari khaatir kon ja kar dekhega ke abu-Jahal ka kya bana ? is par Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) chaley gaey, unhon-ne dekha ke Ifra ke do betey usko talwaaron ka nishana bana chukey hain. aur uska jism thanda ho raha hai. Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne uski dadhi pakad kar kaha : to abu-Jahal hai? abu-Jahal ne kaha : kya us se badey kisi shakhs ko bhi tum ne qatl kiya hai? ya kaha, padhi. uski qaum ne qatl kiya hai? ( Sulaiman Taimi ne) kaha : abu-Mujliz ne kaha : abu-Jahal ne ye bhi kaha tha : kaash! ! mujhey kisaanon ke ilawa kisi aur ne qatl kiya hota."
4663,"hamein Moatamir ne kaha : maine apne walid ( Sulaiman Taimi ( se suna, wo keh rahe they : hamein Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mere liye kon malum karega ke abu-Jahal ka kya hua? aagey ibne-Ulaih ki hadis aur abu-Mujliz ke qaul ki tarah hai, jis tarah Ismail ne bayan kiya hai."
4664,"hamein Sufiyan ne Amr se hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Kab-bin-Ashraf ki zimme-dari kon lega? us ne Allah aur uske rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko azeeyat di hai. Muhammad-bin-Muslima (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Allah ke rasool ! kya aap chahtey hain ke main usey qatl kar dun? aap ne farmaya : haan. unhon-ne kaha : mujhey ijazat dijiye ki main (ye kaam kartey huey) koi baat keh loon. aap ne farmaya : keh lenaa. chunanche wo uske paas aaey, baat ki aur baahami ta'lluqaat ka tazkira kiya aur kaha : ye aadmi sadqa ( lena ( chahta hai aur hamein takleef mein daal diya hai. jab us ne ye suna to kehney laga : Allah ki qism ! tum aur bhi uktaao gey . unhon-ne kaha : ab to ham uske perokar bin chukey hain aur) abhi ( usey chhodnaa nahi chahtey. yahan tak ke dekh lein ke uske mamley ka anjam kya hota hai. kaha : main chahta hun ke tum mujhey kuchh udhaar do. usne kaha : tum mere paas girwi mein kya rakho gey? unhon-ne jawab diya : tum kya chahtey ho? usne kaha : apni aurton ko mere paas girwi rakh do. unhon-ne kaha : tum Arab ke sabse khoobsurat insan ho, kya ham apni auratein tumharey paas girwi rakhein? us ne unse kaha : tum apne bachchey mere yahan girwi rakh do. unhon-ne kaha : ham mein se kisi ke betey ko gaali di jaeygi to kaha jaeyga : wo khajoor ke do wasaq ke iwaz girwi rakha gaya tha. albatta ham tumharey paas zirah yani hathiyar girwi rakh detey hain. usne kaha : theek hai. unhon-ne us se wada kiya ke wo Haris , abu-Abas-bin-jabr aur Ibaad-bin-Bishr (Raziallahu anhu) ko lekar uske paas aaeingey. kaha : wo aaey aur raat ke waqt usey awaz di to wo utar kar unke paas aaya. Sufiyan ne kaha : Amr ke ilawa doosrey rawi ne kaha : uski biwi us se kehney lagi : main aisi awaz sun rahi hun jaisey wo khoon (ke talabgaar ( ki awaz ho. usne kaha : ye to Muhammad-bin-Mussalima (Raziallahu anhu) aur uska doodh Sharik bhai aur abu-Naeyla (Raziallahu anhu) hain aur Karim insan ko raat ke waqt bhi kisi zakhm (ke madaawey ( ki khaatir bulaya jaey to wo aata hai. Muhammad (bin mussalima (Raziallahu anhu)) ne (apne sathiyon se) kaha : main, jab wo aayega , apna hath uske sar ki taraf badhaaun ga , jab main usey khub achi tarah jakad loon to wo tumharey bas mein hoga (tum apna kaam kar guzarna .) kaha : jab wo nichey utra to is tarah utra ke usne peti ( chadar baain kandhey par daal kar uska sar daain baghl ke nichey se nikal kar seeney par donon siron se) baandhi hui thi. unhon-ne kaha : hamein aap se itr ki khushbu aa rahi hai. usne kaha : haan , mere nikah mein falan aurat hai, wo Arab ki sab aurton se zyada muattar (khushbudar) rehney wali hai. unhon-ne kaha : kya tum mujhey ijazat detey ho ke main is ( khushbu ( ko soongh loon ? usne kaha : haan , soongh lo. to unhon-ne ( sar ko) pakad kar soonghaa . phir kaha : kya tum mujhey ijazat detey ho ke main isey dobara soongh loon? kaha : to unhon-ne uske sar ko qaabu kar liya, phir kaha : tumharey bas mein hai. kaha : to unhon-ne usey qatl kar diya."
4665,"Abdul-Azeez-bin-Suhaib ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khaibar ki jang ladi. ham ne wahan subah ki Namaz andherey mein padhi. phir Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sawar huey aur abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) bhi sawar huey aur main sawari par abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ke peechhey tha. Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khaibar ke tang raston main apni sawari ko daudaayaa , mera ghutna Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki raan ko chhu raha tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki raan se kapda hat gaya aur main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki raan ki safedi dekh raha tha. jab aap basti mein dakhil huey to farmaya : Allahu-akbar ! khaibar tabah hua, ham jab kisi qaum ke gharon ke samney utartey hain to un logon ki subah buri hoti hai jinhein ( aaney se pahley) daraaya gaya tha. aap ne teen baar yahi farmaya. kaha : log apne kaamon ke liye nikal chukey they, to unhon-ne kaha : (ye ( Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hain. Abdul-Azeez ne kaha : hamarey kuchh sathiyon ne kaha : aur lashkar hai. kaha : ham ne usey bazor shamsheer hasil kiya.(talwaron ke bal par)"
4666,"Sabit ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : khaibar ke din main sawari par Hazrat abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ke peechhey tha aur mera paon Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paon ko chhu raha tha. kaha : ham us waqt unke paas pahunchey jab suraj chamak raha tha, wo log apne maweshi nikal chukey they aur kulhaadiyaan, tokriyaan aur belchey lekar ( khud bhi) nikal chukey they. to unhon-ne kaha : Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hain aur lashkar hai. kaha : to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : khaibar ujad gaya, jab ham kisi qaum ke gharon ke samney utartey hain to un logon ki subah buri hoti hai jinhein daraayaa ja chuka tha. kaha : to izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne unhein shikast di."
4667,"Qatada ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khaibar aaey to aap ne farmaya : jab ham kisi qaum ke gharon ke aagey utartey hain to daraaiye gaey logon ki subah buri hoti hai."
4668,"Qutaiba-bin-Saeed aur Muhammad-bin-Ibad ne. padhi. alfaz ibne-Ibad ke hain. padhi. hamein hadis bayan ki, un donon ne kaha : hamein Hatim-bin-Ismail ne Salma-bin-Akwa (Raziallahu anhu) ke aazad karda ghulam Yazeed-bin-abi-Ubaid se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Salma-bin-Akwa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath khaibar ki taraf rawaana huey to ham ne raat ke waqt safar kiya, logon mein se aik aadmi ne Aamir-bin-Akwaa (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : kya tum hamein apne naadir jangi ashaar  nahi sunao gey? aur Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) shaair aadmi they. wo utar kar logon ke) oonton (ke liye hoodi parhney lagey. wo keh rahe they : aey Allah ! agar to ( Fazal aur karam karne wala ( na hota to ham hidayat na patey, na sadqa kartey, na Namaz padhtey, ham terey naam par qurbaan, ham ne jo gunah kiye unko bakhsh de aur agar hamara muqaabla ho to hamarey qadam jama de aur ham par zaroor sakeenat aur waqaar nazil farmaa. hamein jab bhi awaz de kar bulaya gaya ham aaey, hamein awaz de kar un ( awaz dene waale) logon ne ham par aitimad kiya. (aur ham is par poorey utrey .) to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha : ye (hoodi padhkar) oonton ko haankney wala kon hai? logon ne kaha : Aamir . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( Allah se uski mohabbat aur shauq ko dekhtey huey) farmaya : Allah is par raham karey ! logon mein se aik aadmi (Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : (iske liye shahadat ( wajib ho gaee. aey Allah ke rasool ! aap ne (uske haq mein dua muakhkhar farma kar) hamein us (ki sohbat ( se zyada muddat fayda kyon nahi uthaney diya ? ( Salma-bin-Akwa (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : ham khaibar pahunchey to ham ne unka muhaasra kar liya yahan tak ke hamein (shadeed bhook ke) makhmasey ne aa liya. iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : bila shubah Allah ne usey un (jihad karne waale) logon ke liye fateh kar diya hai. jab logon ne us din ki Sham ki, jab unhein fateh ata ki gaee thi to unhon-ne bahut si ( jaghon par) aag jalaaii. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha : ye aag kaisi hai aur ye log kis cheez (ko pakaaney (ke liye usey jalaa rahe hain? unhon-ne jawab diya : gosht (ko pakaaney (ke liye. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha : kon sa gosht? unhon-ne jawab diya : paaltu gadhon ka gosht. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : usey (pani samet) baha do aur un ( bartanon ( ko tod do. is par aik aadmi ne kaha : ya usey baha dein aur bartan dho lein? to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ya aisey kar lo. kaha : jab logon ne mil kar saf bandi ki to Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) ki talwaar chhoti thi, unhon-ne maarney ke liye us ( talwaar ( se aik Yahudi ki pindli ko nishana banaya to talwaar ki dhaar lot kar Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghutney par aa lagi aur wo usi zakhm se faut ho gaey. jab log wapas huey, Salma (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aur us waqt unhon-ne mera hath pakda hua tha, kaha : jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey khamosh dekha to aap ne puchha : tumhen kya hua hai? maine aap se kaha : mere maan-baap aap par qurbaan ! logon ka khayal hai ke Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) ka amal zaaya ho gaya hai. aap ne farmaya : kis ne kaha hai? maine kaha : falan , falan aur Usaid-bin-Huzair Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ne. to aap ne farmaya : jisne bhi ye kaha, ghalat kaha hai, uske liye to yaqinan do ajr hain. aap ne apni donon ungliyon ko ikattha kiya. wo to khud jam kar jihad karne waley Mujahid they, kam hi koi arabi hoga jo us rastey par unki tarah chala hoga. Quteba ne hadis ke do harfon ( القين (ke aakhiri do harfon ی aur ن ( mein Muhammad (bin-Ibad) ki mukhalifat ki hai aur (Muhammad ( bin-Ibad ki riwayat main ( القين (ke bajaey) ( الق )) ( zaroor biz-zaroor ki takeed ke baghair mahz ( nazil karke alfaz hain."
4669,"abu-Taahir ne mujhey hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein ibne-Wahab ne khabar di, kaha : mujhey Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se khabar di, kaha : mujhey Abdur-Rehman ne khabar di. padhi. ibne-Wahab ke ilawa doosrey rawi ne unka nasb bayan kiya to (Abdur-Rehman) bin-Abdullah-bin-Kab-bin-Malik ne kaha, padhi. ke Hazrat Salma-bin-Akwa (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : jab khaibar ka din tha, mere bhai ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath khub jang ladi, (usi beech mein) unki talwaar palat kar unhi ko ja lagi aur unhein Shahid kar diya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaba ne us hawale se kuchh baatein kahin aur us mamley mein shak (ka izhar kiya) ke aadmi apne hi aslaha se faut hua hai. unhon-ne unke mamley ke kuchh pahluon mein shak kiya. Salma (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khaibar se wapas huey to maine kaha : aey Allah ke rasool ! mujhey ijazat dijiye ki main aap ke aagey rajziya (fakhriya) ashaar padhun to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein ijazat de di. is par Hazrat Umar-bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main janta hun jo tum kehney ja rahe ho. kaha : to maine (ye rajziya (fakhriya) ashaar ( padhey : Allah ki qism ! agar Allah (ka karam ( na hota to ham hidayat na patey , na sadqa kartey aur na Namaz padhtey . is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum ne sach kaha, ham par bahut sakeenat nazil farma aur agar hamara muqaabla ho to hamarey qadam mazbut kar de, mushrikon ne yaqinan ham par sakht zyadti ki. kaha : jab maine apne rajziya (fakhriya) ashaar khatm kiye to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha : ye ( ashaar ( kis ne kahey ? maine jawab diya : mere bhai ne kahey . to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah un par raham karey ! kaha : to maine kaha : Allah ki qism ! Allah ke rasool ! kuchh log uske liye dua kartey huey dar rahe they, wo keh rahe they : wo aadmi apne hi aslahey se faut hua hai. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : wo to jihad kartey huey Mujahid ke taur par faut hua hai. ibne-Shahab ne kaha : phir maine Salma-bin-Akwa (Raziallahu anhu) ke aik betey se sawal kiya to unhon-ne mujhey apne walid se usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki, magar unhon-ne (Hazrat Salma (Raziallahu anhu) ke alfaz dohraatey huey) kaha : jab maine kaha : kuchh log uske liye dua karne se dartey hain to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : un logon ne ghalat kaha, wo to jihad kartey huey Mujahid ke taur par faut huey, unke liye dohra ajr hai. aur aap ne apni do ungliyon se ishara farmaya."
4670,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Shoba ne Abu-Ishaq se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne kaha : ehzaab ke din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamarey sath mitti utha kar phenk rahe they. (us) mitti ne batan Mubarak (pait) ki safedi ko chipa liya tha aur aap farma rahe they : Allah ki qism ! agar tera karam na hota to ham hidayat na patey , na sadqa kartey, na Namaz padhtey . ham par zaroor biz-zaroor sakeenat nazil farmaa. un logon ne ham par zulm kiya hai. kaha : kabhi-kabhi aap farmatey : un sardaaron ne ham par) apna zulm rokney se) inkar kar diya, jab wo fitney ka irada kartey hain ham us (main padney ( se inkar kar detey hain. aap un (alfaz ( par apni awaz ko buland farma letey."
4671,"Abdur-Rehman-bin-Mehdi ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Shoba ne Abu-Ishaq se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) se suna. padhi. unhon-ne usi ki tarah bayan kya, albatta (is riwayat ke mutabiq ( unhon-ne kaha : bila shubah un logon ne ham par zyadti ki hai."
4672,"Hazrat Sahal-bin-Sad (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamarey paas tashrif laey jabke ham khandaq khod rahe they aur apne kandhon par mitti utha kar phenk rahe they, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aey Allah ! zindagi to sirf aakhirat ki zindagi hai, isliye muhajireen aur Ansar ki maghfirat farma."
4673,"Muawiya bin Qurra ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : aey Allah ! aakhirat ki zindagi ke siwa koi zindagi nahi, to Ansar aur muhajireen ko maaf farma de."
4674,"Shoba ne hamein Qatada se hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmatey they : aey Allah ! be-shak zindagi aakhirat ki zindagi hai. Shoba ne kaha : ya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne yun farmaya : aey Allah ! aakhirat ki zindagi ke siwa koi zindagi ( haqiqi ( nahi, to Ansar aur muhajireen ko izzat ata farma."
4675,"Yahya-bin-Yahya aur Sheban-bin-Farukh ne hamein hadis bayan ki, Yahya ne kaha : hamein Abdul-Waris ne Abu-Tayyah se hadis bayan ki, kaha : Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamein hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : sahaba rajziya ashaar padhtey they aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unka sath detey they, wo kehtey they : aey Allah ! bhalai to sirf aakhirat ki bhalai hai, to Ansar aur muhajireen ki madad farma. Sheban ki hadis mein madad farma ki jagah maghfirat farma hai."
4676,"Hammaad-bin-Salma ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Sabit ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki ke khandaq ke din Muhammad (Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)) ke sahaba keh rahe they : ham wo log hain jinhoney Islam par zindagi bhar ke liye Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bait ki. ya kaha : jihad par. padhi. Hammad ko shak hua hai. aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmatey they : aey Allah ! asl bhalai, aakhirat ki bhalai hai, to Ansar aur muhajireen ki maghfirat farma."
4677,"Salma bin Akwa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai main subah ki azan se pahley nikla aur aap ki dodheli oontniyan zi-Qard mein charti thin (zi-Qard aik pani ka naam hai Madina se aik din ke fasla par. Bukhari ne kaha ye ladai khaibar ki jang se teen din pahley hui aur kuch ne kaha 6 hijri mein Hudaibiya se pahley) mujhey Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ka ghulam mila usne kaha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki dudheli oontniyan jati rahen. maine puchha kis ne lin? usne kaha Ghatfan ne (jo aik shaakh hai Qais qabeele ki). ye sun kar main teen baar chillaya ya sabaaha (arab ki aadat hai ke ye kalima us waqt kehtey hain jab koi badi aafat aati hai aur logon ko khabardaar karne ki zarurat hoti hai) aur Madina ke donon taraf walon ko suna diya phir main seedha chala yahan tak ke maine un luteron ko zi-Qard mein paya unhon-ne pani peena shuru kya tha maine teer maarna shuru kiye aur main teerandaaz tha aur kehta jata tha main ibne-Akwa hun aur aaj maaon ka doodh pinewalon ka din hai. main rajz padhta raha yahan tak ke oontniyan unse chhuda lin balke aur tees chaadrein unki chheenin aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur log bhi aa gaey. maine arz kya ya Rasulullah un luteron ko maine pani peeney nahi diya, wo piyaasey hain ab un par lashkar ko bhejiye . aap ne farmaya aey Akwaa ke betey ! to apni cheezein ley chuka ab janey de. Salma (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha phir ham lautey aur Rasulullah ne ontni par apne sath mujh ko bithlaaya yahan tak ke ham Madina mein pahunchey."
4678,"saiyedna ibne- Akwaa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, jab ham Hudaibiya mein pahunchey so ham chaudah so aadmi they ( yahi mashhoo riwayat hai aur aik riwayat mein 1300 aur aik riwayat mein pandarah so aaey hain) aur wahan pachaas bakriyan thin jinko kuwein ka pani sair na kar sakta tha (yani aisa kam pani tha kuwein mein) phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kuwein ke mendh par baithey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dua ki ya thooka kuwein mein wo us waqt ubal aaya. phir ham ne janwaron ko pani pilaya aur khud bhi piyaa . baad iske Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ham ko bulaya bait ke liye darakht ki jad mein (usi darakht ko shajra rizwaan kehtey hain aur us darakht ka zikr Quran sharif mein hai. ( إِنَّ الَّذِينَ يُبَايِعُونَكَ إِنَّمَا يُبَايِعُونَ اللَّـهَ يَدُ اللَّـهِ فَوْقَ أَيْدِيهِمْ فَمَن نَّكَثَ فَإِنَّمَا يَنكُثُ عَلَىٰ نَفْسِهِ وَمَنْ أَوْفَىٰ بِمَا عَاهَدَ عَلَيْهُ اللَّـهَ فَسَيُؤْتِيهِ أَجْرًا عَظِيمًا Mina ( ۴۸ / fateh : 10 ( maine sabse pahley logon mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bait ki. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bait letey rahe letey rahe, yahan tak ke aadhey aadmi bait kar chukey. us waqt Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey Salma bait kar. maine arz kya, ya Rasulullah ! main to aap se awwal hi bait kar chuka . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : '' phir sahi''aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey nihatta (be hathiyar) dekha to aik badi si dhaal ya chhoti si dhaal di, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bait leney lagey, yahan tak ke log khatm honey lagey, us waqt Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey Salma ! mujh se bait nahi kartaa.'' maine arz kya, ya Rasulullah ! main to aap ki bait kar chuka awwal logon mein, phir beech ke logon mein. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : '' phir sahi'' , gharaz maine teesri baar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bait ki. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey Salma ! teri wo badi dhaal ya chhoti dhaal kahan hai jo maine tujhey di thi. '' maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! mera chacha Aamir mujhey mila, wo nihatta tha maine wo phir usko de di. ye sun kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : '' teri misal us agley shakhs ki si hui jisne dua ki thi ya Allah ! mujhey aisa dost de jis ko main apni jaan se zyada chaahun.'' phir mushrikon ne suleh ke payaam bhejey yahan tak ke har aik taraf ke aadmi dusri taraf janey lagey aur ham ne suleh kar li, Salma ne kaha : main Talha bin Ubaidullah ki khidmat mein tha, unke ghodey ko pani pilaata, unki peeth khujaata, unki khidmat karta, unhi ke sath khana khata aur maine apna ghar baar, dhan-daulat sab chhod diya tha, Allah aur uske rasool ki taraf hijrat ki jab hamari aur Makka walon ki suleh ho gaee aur ham mein har aik-doosrey se milney laga to main aik darakht ke paas aaya aur uske taley se kaantey jhaadey aur jad ke paas leta . itney mein char aadmi mushrikon mein se aaey Makka walon mein se aur lagey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko bura kehney . mujhey ghussa aaya, main doosrey darakht ke nichey chala gaya, unhon-ne apne hathiyar latkaey aur let rahe, wo usi haal mein they ke yakaayak wadi ke nasheb se kisi ne awaz di, daudo aey muhajireen! ibne- zaneem ( sahabi ( maarey gaey. ye suntey hi maine apni talwaar soonti aur un charon aadmiyon par hamla kya, wo so rahe they, unke hathiyar maine ley liye aur gatha bana kar aik hath mein rakhey, phir maine kaha : qism uski jisne izzat di Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke munh ko, tum mein se jisne sar uthaya , main aik mar doonga us uzu (khaas ang) par jis mein uski donon aankhen hain. phir main unko kheenchta hua laya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aur mera chacha Aamir ablaat (eik shaakh hai Quraish ki) mein se aik shakhs ko laya jis ko makooz kehtey they wo usko kheenchta hua laya ghodey par, jis par jhul padi thi aur 70 aadmiyon ke sath mushrikon mein se. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unko dekha. phir farmaya : ''chhod do unko . mushrikon ki taraf se ahad shikani shuru honey do. phir dobara bhi unhi ki taraf se honey do. '' (yani ham agar un logon ko maarein to suleh ke baad hamari taraf se ahad shikani hogi ye munasib nahi pahley kaafiron ki taraf se ahad shikani ho aik baar nahi 2 baar tab ham ko badla lena bura nahi ( aakhir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne un logon ko maaf kar diya. tab Allah Taala ne ye aayat utari ( وَهُوَ الَّذِي كَفَّ أَيْدِيَهُمْ عَنكُمْ وَأَيْدِيَكُمْ عَنْهُم بِبَطْنِ مَكَّةَ مِن بَعْدِ أَنْ أَظْفَرَكُمْ عَلَيْهِمْ Mina ( ۴۸ / fateh : ۲۴ ( akheer tak '' yani us Allah ne unke hathon ko roka tum se aur tumharey hathon ko roka unse Makka ki sarhad mein jab fateh de chuka tha tum ko un par. '' phir ham lautey Madina ko , raah mein aik manzil par utrey , jahan hamarey aur bani Lahyaan ke mushrikon ke beech mein aik pahaad tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dua ki us shakhs ke liye jo us pahaad par chadh jaey raat ko aur pahra de aap ka aur aap ke ashaab kaa. Salma ne kaha : main raat ko us pahaad par 2 ya teen baar chadha (aur pahra deta raha), phir ham Madina mein pahunchey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni oontniyan apne Ribah ghulam ko din aur main bhi uske sath tha, Talha ka ghoda liye huey charaagaah mein pahunchaney ke liye un oontniyon ke sath, jab subah hui to Abdur-Rehman fazari (mushrik) ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki oontniyon ko loot liya aur sabko haank ley gaya aur charwaahey ko mar dala. maine kaha : aey Ribaah! to ye ghoda ley aur Talha ke paas pahuncha de aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko khabar karke kaafiron ne aap ki oontniyan loot lin, phir main aik teele par khada hua aur Madina ki taraf munh karke maine teen baar awaz di (ya sabaaha) baad iske main un luteron ke peechhey rawana hua teer maarta hua aur rajz padhta hua yani ''main Akwaa ka betaa hun aur aaj kameenon ki tabahi ka din hai.'' phir main kisi ke qareeb hota aur aik teer uski kaathi mein maarta jo uske kaandhey tak pahunch jata (kaathi ko cheer kar) aur kehta ye ley aur main Akwaa ka betaa hun aur aaj kameenon ki tabahi ka din hai, phir qism Allah ki main barabar teer maarta raha aur zakhmi karta raha jab unmein se koi sawar meri taraf laut-taa to main darakht ke taley aa kar uski jad mein baith jata aur aik teer maarta wo sawar zakhmi ho jata yahan tak ke wo pahaad ke tang rastey mein ghusey aur main pahaad par chadh gaya aur wahan se patthar maarna shuru kiye aur barabar unka peechha karta raha yahan tak ke koi oont jisko Allah Taala ne paida kya tha aur wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sawari ka tha na bacha jo mere peechhey na reh gaya aur luteron ne usko na chhod diya ho (to sab oont saiyedna Salma-bin-Akwa (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse chheen liye) Salma ne kaha : phir main unke peechhey chala, teer maarta hua yahan tak ke tees chaadaron mein se zyada aur tees bhaalon se zyada unse chheenin wo apne tain halka kartey they (bhaagney ke liye) aur jo cheez wo phainktey main is par aik nishan rakh deta patthar ka taake Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ashaab usko pehchan lein (ke ye ghaneemat ka maal hai aur usko ley lein) yahan tak ke wo aik tang ghaati mein aaey aur wahan unko badr fazari ka beta mila, wo sab baithey subah ka naashta karne lagey aur main aik chhoti teekri ki choti par betha. Fazari ne kaha : ye kon shakhs hai. wo boley us shakhs ne ham ko tang kar diya. qism Allah ki andheri raat se hamarey sath hai barabar teer maarey jata hai yahan tak ke jo kuchh hamarey paas tha sab chheen liya. fazari ne kaha : tum mein se char aadmi usko ja kar mar lein. ye sun kar char aadmi meri taraf chadhey pahaad par jab wo itney door aagey ke meri baat sun sakein to maine kaha : tum mujhey jantey ho. unhon-ne kaha : nahi, maine kaha : main Salma hun, Akwaa ka betaa (Akwaa unke dada they lekin dada ki taraf apne ko mansub kya b-wajah shohrat ke aur Salma ke bap ka naam Amr tha aur Aamir unke chacha they kyonkey wo Akwaa ke betey they) qism us zaat ki jisne buzurgi di Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke munh Mubarak ko main tum mein se jis ko chaahunga mar daalunga (teer se) aur tum mein se koi mujhey nahi mar sakta , unmein aik shakhs bola. ye aisa hi malum hota hai phir wo sab lautey. main wahan se nahi chala tha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sawar nazar aaey jo darakhton mein ghus rahe they. sabse aagey Akhram Asadi they, unke peechhey abu-Qatada unke peechhey Miqdaad-bin-Aswad kandi. maine Akhram ke ghodey ki baag thaam li, ye dekh kar wo luterey bhaagey. maine kaha : aey Akhram tum unse bachey rehna aisa na ho ye tum ko mar daalein jab tak Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ashaab na aa lein. unhon-ne kaha : aey Salma ! agar tujh ko yaqin hai Allah ka aur aakhirat ke din ka aur to janta hai ke jannat sach hai aur jahannam sach hai to mat rok mujh ko shahadat se. (yani bahut hoga to yahi ke main un logon ke hath Shahid hunga us se kya behtar hai) maine unko chhod diya, unka muqaabla hua Abdur-Rehman fazari , se Akhram ne iske ghodey ko zakhmi kya aur Abdur-Rehman ne barchhi se Akhram ko Shahid kya aur Akhram ke ghodey par chadh betha , itney mein saiyedna abu-Qatada Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke shehsawaar aan pahunchey aur unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman ko barchhi mar kar qatl kya to qism uski jisne buzurgi di Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke munh Mubarak ko main unka peechha kiya gaya, main apne paon se aisa daud raha tha ke mujhey apne peechhey aap ka koi sahabi na dikhlai diya na unka ghubaar yahan tak ke wo luterey aaftaab doobney se pahley aik ghaati mein pahunchey jahan pani tha aur uska naam zi -Qard tha, wo utrey pani peeney ko piyaasey they, phir mujhey dekha, mein unke peechhey daudta chala aata tha aakhir maine unko pani par se hata diya wo aik qatra bhi na pi sakey, ab wo daudtey chaley kisi ghaati ki taraf. main bhi douda aur unmein se kisi ko paakar aik teer laga diya iske shaaney ki haddi main aur maine kaha : ley usko aur main betaa hun Akwaa ka aur ye din kameenon ki tabahi ka hai. wo bola ( Allah karey Akwaa ka betaa marey aur) uski maan is par roey . kya wahi Akwaa hai jo subah ko mere sath tha. maine kaha : haan aey dushman apni jaan ke wahi Akwaa hai jo subah ko terey sath tha. Salma-bin-Akwa ne kaha : un luteron ke 2 ghodey saqat ho gaey ( daudtey daudtey ( unhon-ne unko chhod diya aik ghaati mein, main un ghodon ko kheenchta hua Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas laya. wahan mujh ko Aamir miley aik chhaagal doodh ki pani mila hua aur aik chhaagal pani ki liye huey, maine wuzu kya aur doodh piyaa ( Allahu-akbar ! Salma-bin-Akwa ki himmat subah sawerey se daudtey daudtey raat ho gaee ghodey thak gaey, oont thak gaey, log mar gaey, asbaab reh gaya par Salma na thakey aur din bhar mein kuchh khaya na piyaa Allah jalle-jalalahu ki imdaad thi) phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us pani par they jahan se maine luteron ko bhagaaya tha. maine dekha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sab oont ley liye hain aur sab cheezein jo maine mushrikon se chheeni thin sab barchhi aur chaadrein aur saiyedna Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ne un oonton mein se jo maine chheeni thi aik oont nehar kya aur wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye uski kaleji aur kohan bhoon rahe hain. maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah! dijiye mujh ko ijazat lashkar mein se so aadmi chun leney ki phir main luteron ka peechhaa karta hun aur unmein se koi shakhs baqi nahi rahe jo khabar de apni qaum ko ja kar (yani sab ko mar daalta hun) ye sun kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hansey , yahan tak daadhein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khul gain angaar ki roshni mein. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey Salma! to ye kar sakta hai.'' maine kaha : haan! qism uski jisne aapko buzurgi di. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo to ab Ghatfan ki sarhad mein pahunch gaey wahan unki mehmani ho rahi hai.'' itney mein aik shakhs aaya Ghatfan mein se. wo bola : falan shakhs ne unke liye aik oont kaata tha wo uski khaal nikal rahe they. itney mein unko gard malum hui. wo kehney lagey log aagey to wahan se bhi bhag khadey huey. jab subah hui to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aaj ke din hamarey sawaaron mein behtar sawar abu-Qatada hain aur piyaadon mein sabse badh kar Salma-bin-Akwa hain.'' Salma ne kaha : phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh ko 2 hisse diye. aik hissey sawar ka aur aik hissey piyaadey ka aur donon mujh hi ko de diye. baad iske Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey apne sath bithaya azba par Madina ko laut-tey waqt. ham chal rahe they ke aik Ansari jo daudney mein kisi se peechhey nahi rehta tha kehney laga koi hai jo Madina ko mujh se aagey daud jaey aur baar-baar yahi kehta tha jab maine uska kehna suna to us se kaha to buzurg ki buzurgi nahi karta aur buzurg se nahi darta. wo bola : nahi, albatta Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki buzurgi karta hun. maine arz kya ya Rasulullah! mere maan-baap aap par fida hon, mujhey chhod dijiye main us mard se aagey badhunga daud mein. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''achchha agar tera ji chaahey.'' tab maine kaha, main aata hun teri taraf aur maine apna paon tedha kya aur kood pada phir main douda aur jab aik ya 2 chadhaao baqi rahe to dam ko sanbhaala phir jo douda to us se mil gaya. yahan tak ke aik ghoonsa diya maine uske donon moondhon ke beech mein aur maine kaha : qism Allah ki ab main aagey badha phir us se aagey pahuncha Madina ko (to malum hua ke muqaabla durust hai bila-ewaz aur b-ewaz mein khilaf hai) phir qism Allah ki ham sirf teen raat thahrey baad iske khaibar ki taraf nikley Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath to mere chacha Aamir ne rajz padhna shuru kya. '' qism Allah ki agar Allah hidayat na karta to ham raah na patey aur na sadqa detey, na Namaz padhtey aur ham terey Fazal se be-parwaa nahi huey to jama rakh hamarey paon ko agar kaafiron se milen aur apni rehmat aur tasalli utaar hamarey uper. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye kon hai? '' logon ne kaha : Aamir . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah bakhshey tujh ko .'' Salma (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab kisi ke liye khas taur par istighfar kartey to wo zaroor Shahid hota to saiyedna umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne pukara aur wo apne oont par they. ya Nabi Allah ! aap ne ham ko fayda kyon na uthaney diya Aamir se, saiyedna Salma (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : phir jab ham khaibar mein aaey to uska badshah Marhab talwaar hilata hua nikla aur ye rajz padhta tha ki ""Khaibar ko malum hai ke main marhab hun pura hathiyar band bahaadur aazmooda kaar jab ladaaiyaan aaein sholey udaati hui.'' ye sun kar mere chacha Aamir nikley uske muqable ke liye aur unhon-ne ye rajz padha ki ""Khaibar janta hai ke main Aamir hun. hathiyar band ladai mein ghusney wala.'' phir donon ka eik-eik waar hua to marhab ki talwaar mere chacha Aamir ki dhaal par padi aur Aamir ne nichey se waar karna chaha to unki talwaar unhi ko aa lagi aur sheh-rag kat gaee usi se mar gaey. saiyedna Salma (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : phir main nikla to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chand ashaab ko dekha wo keh rahe hain Aamir ka amal laghw ho gaya us ne apne tain aap mar dala. ye sun kar main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya rota hua. maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! Aamir ka amal laghw ho gaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : '' kon kehta hai.'' maine kaha : aap ke ashaab kehtey hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jhoot kaha jisne kaha balke usko dohra sawab hai.'' phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh ko saiyedna Ali-bin abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas bheja unki aankhen dukh rahi thin. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main aisey shakhs ko jhanda doonga jo dost rakhta hai Allah aur uske rasool ko ya Allah aur rasool usko dost rakhtey hain.'' ( ibne- Hisham ki riwayat mein itna zyada hai ke Allah fateh dega uske hathon par aur wo bhaagney wala nahi) Salma (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : phir main saiyedna Ali-bin abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaya aur unko liya kheenchta hua unki aankhen dukh rahi thin yahan tak ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas ley aaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unki aankhon mein apna luaabe-dahan daal diya wo usi waqt achchhey ho gaey. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unko nishan diya aur marhab nikla aur kehney laga ‏‏‏‏قَدْ عَلِمَتْ خَيْبَرُ أَنِّى مَرْحَبُ شَاكِى السِّلاَحِ بَطَلٌ مُجَرَّبُ إِذَا الْحُرُوبُ أَقْبَلَتْ تَلَهَّبُ . saiyedna Ali-bin abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ne iske jawab mein, ye kaha ( أَنَا الَّذِى سَمَّتْنِى أُمِّى حَيْدَرَهْ كَلَيْثِ غَابَاتٍ كَرِيهِ الْمَنْظَرَهْ أُوفِيهِمُ بِالصَّاعِ كَيْلَ السَّنْدَرَهْ ( '' yani mein wo hon ke meri maan ne mera naam haidar rakha. misl us sher ke jo jangalon mein hota hai (yani sher babbar) bahut hi zyada daraawni sura (ke iske dekhney se khof paida ho) mein logon ko aik saa ke badley teeron ka poora ped deta hun. (yani wo to mere uper halka hamla kartey hain aur main unka kaam hi tamam kar deta hun) phir saiyedna Ali-bin abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ne marhab ke sar par aik chot lagai aur wo usi waqt jahannam ko rawaana hua. baad iske Allah Taala ne fateh di unke hathon par. aik aur sanad ke sath saiyedna Ikrima bin Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye hadis us hadis se bhi zyada tafseel se naql ki hai. aur dusri mein isi tarah hai."
4679,"saiyedna Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai assii (80) aadmi Makka waley Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke uper utrey taneem ke pahaad se, wo chahtey they Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dhokaa dein aur ghafalat mein hamla karein. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unko pakad liya aur qaid kiya, baad iske Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chhod diya. tab Allah Taala ne is aayat ko utara :                     ( وَهُوَ الَّذِي كَفَّ أَيْدِيَهُمْ عَنْكُمْ )                                                                                                                                                          ''yani Allah wo hai jisne rokaa unke hathon ko tum se (aur unka faraib kuchh na chala (aur tumharey hathon ko unse (tum ne unko qatl na kiya ( Makka ki sarhad main tumharey fateh ho janey ke baad un par.''"
4680,"Sabit ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Hunain ke din Hazrat Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) ne aik khanjar (apne paas rakh ( liya, wo unke sath tha, Hazrat abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey dekh liya to unhon-ne kaha : Allah ke rasool ! ye Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) hain, inke paas aik khanjar hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse puchha : ye khanjar kaisa hai? unhon-ne kaha : maine ye isliye liya hai ke agar mushrikon mein se koi mere qareeb aaya to main is se uska pet chaak kar dun gii. (ye sun kar) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hansney lagey. unhon-ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool ! hamarey baad daayra Islam mein shamil honey waale, jinhein (fatah Makka ke din) maafi di gaee thi ( Hunain ke din) aapko chhod kar bhag gaey, unhein qatl karwaa dijiye. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Umme-Sulaim ! bila shubah Allah Taala kafi ho gaya ( unka bhagna jang haarney ka baais na bana (aur us ne ehsan farmaya. (ke hamein fateh ata kar di.)"
4681,Ishaq-bin-Abdullah-bin-abi-Talha ne (apne chacha (Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se (apni daadi ( Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) ke waqiey ke hawale se Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Sabit ki hadis ki tarah riwayat ki.
4682,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab jang kartey to Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) aur Ansar ki kuchh dusri aurton ko sath ley ja kar jang kartey, wo pani pilaatin aur zakhmiyon ki marham patti karti thin."
4683,"Abdul-Azeez-bin-Suhaib ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : jab ahad ka din tha, logon mein se kuchh log Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko chhod kar paspaa ho gaey aur Hazrat abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney aik dhaal ke sath aad kiye huey they. abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) intihai quwwat se teer chalaney waley teer andaz they. unhon-ne us din do ya teen kamaanein todin. kaha : koi shakhs apne sath teeron ka tarkash liye huey guzarta to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmatey : usey abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ke aagey phaila do. kaha : Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) logon ka jaaiza leney ke liye jhank kar dekhtey to abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) arz kartey : Allah ke Nabi ! mere maan-baap aap par qurbaan ! jhank kar na dekhein. kahin dushman ke teeron mein se koi teer aapko na lag jaey. mera Sina aap ke Sina ke aagey dhaal bana hua hai. kaha : maine Hazrat Aaisha binte-abi-Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) aur Hazrat Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha, un donon ne apne kapdey sametey huey they, mein unki pindliyon ke paazeb dekh raha tha. wo apni kamar par mishkeezey lekar aati thin. ( zakhmiyon ko pani pilaatey-pilaatey ( unke munh mein un ( mushkon ( ko khali kartin thin, phir wapas ho kar unhein bharti thin, phir aatin aur unhein logon ke munh mein farigh karti thin. us din oongh ( janey ( ki bina par abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ke hathon se do ya teen martaba talwaar giri . (shadeed thakaan aur adh-jagey aalim mein bhi wo dhaal bin kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney khadey rahe.)"
4684,"Sulaiman-bin-Bilal ne hamein Jafar-bin-Muhammad se, unhon-ne apne walid se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Yazeed-bin-Hurmuz se riwayat ki ke) Maruf khaariji sardaar ( najda (bin-Aamir hanfi) ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se panch baatein malum karne ke liye khat likha . Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : agar ye dar na hota ke main ilm chipa raha hun to main usey jawab na likhtaa . najda ne unhein likha tha : ammaa ba'd ! mujhey bataiye : kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aurton se madad letey huey jang kartey they? kya aap ghaneemat mein unka hissey rakhtey they? kya aap bachchon ko qatl kartey they? aur ye ke yateem ki yateemi Kab khatm hoti hai? us ne khums ke barey mein) bhi puchha ke) wo kis ka haq hai? to Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne uski taraf ( jawab ( likha : tum ne mujh se malum karne ke liye likha tha : kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aurton se madad letey huey jang kartey they? bila shubah aap unse jang mein madad letey they aur wo zakhmiyon ko marham lagaya karti thin aur unhein ghaneemat (ke maal) se maamooli sa Atiya diya jata tha. raha (ghaneemat ka baa-qaayda) hissey to wo aap ne unke liye nahi nikala. aur yaqinan Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bachchon ko qatl nahi kartey they. lihaza tum bhi bachchon ko qatl na kiya karo. aur tum ne mujh se malum karne ke liye likha tha : yateem ki yateemi Kab khatm hoti hai? mujhey apni umr (ke Malik ( ki qism ! kisi aadmi ki dadhi nikal aati hai jabke abhi wo apne liye haq leney mein aur apni taraf se haq dene mein kamzor hota hai, jab wo apne liye theek tarah se huquq ley sakey jis tarah log letey hain to uski yateemi khatm ho jaeygi. aur tum ne mujh se khums ke barey mein malum karne ke liye likha tha ke wo kis ka haq hai? to ham kehtey they : wo hamara haq hai, lekin hamari qaum ne hamari ye baat manney se inkar kar diya."
4685,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim donon ne hamein Hatim-bin-Ismail se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Jafar-bin-Muhammad se, unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Yazeed-bin-Hurmuz se riwayat ki ke najda ne Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ko unse kuchh baatein poochhney ke liye khat likha .) aagey ( Sulaiman-bin-Bilal ki hadis ki tarah hai. magar Hatim ki hadis mein hai : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) yaqinan bachchon ko qatl nahi kartey they, lihaza tum bhi bachchon ko qatl na karo. siwaey-iske ke tumhen bhi isi tarah ilm hasil ho jaey jis tarah khizr (Alaihissalam) ko us bachchey ke barey mein ilm hua tha jisey unhon-ne qatl kiya tha. Ishaq ne Hatim se riwayat ki hui apni hadis mein ye izafa kiya : ( siwaey-iske ke) tum ( bachchon mein se) momin ka imtiyaz (farq) kar lo to kaafir ko qatl kar dena aur momin ko chhod dena (ye donon baatein kisi insan ke bas mein nahi jab tak Allah Taala na bataaey.)"
4686,"hamein ibne-abi-Umar ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Sufiyan ne Ismail-bin-Umayya se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Saeed Maqbari se aur unhon-ne Yazeed-bin-Hurmuz se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : najda-bin-Aamir haroori ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf likha , wo unse us ghulam aur aurat ke barey mein poochh raha tha jo jang mein Sharik hotey hain. kya wo ghaneemat ki taqseem mein (bhi) Sharik hongey? aur bachchon ke qatl karne ke barey mein (poochha (aur yateem ke barey mein ke us se yateemii Kab khatm hoti hai aur rishteydaaron ke barey mein ke wo kon log hain? to unhon-ne Yazeed se kaha : uski taraf likho aur agar dar na hota ke wo kisi himaaqat mein pad jaeyga to main uski taraf jawab na likhtaa. (usey) likho : tum ne mujhey us aurat aur ghulam ke barey malum karne ke liye khat likha tha jo jang mein Sharik hotey hain : kya wo ghaneemat ki taqseem mein Sharik hongey ? haqiqat ye hai ke un donon ke liye kuchh nahi hai. siwaey-iske ke unhein kuchh Atiya de diya jaey. aur tum ne mujh se bachchon ko qatl karne ke barey mein poochhney ke liye likha tha, bila shubah Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein qatl nahi kiya aur tum bhi unhein qatl mat karo, siwaey-iske ke tumhen un bachchon ke barey mein wo baat malum ho jaey jo Hazrat Musa (Alaihissalam) ke sathi ( khizr (Alaihissalam) ( ko us bachchey ke barey mein malum ho gaee jisey unhon-ne qatl kiya tha. aur tum ne mujh se yateem ke barey mein poochhney ke liye likha tha ke us se yateem ka laqab Kab khatm hoga? to haqiqat ye hai ke us se yateem ka laqab khatm nahi hota yahan tak ke wo baligh ho jaey aur uski bulooghat (samajhdaari ki umr ko pahunchne) ke barey pata chalney lagey. aur tum ne mujh se rishteydaaron ke barey mein poochhney ke liye likha tha ke wo kon hain? hamara khayal tha ke wo ham log hi hain. to hamari qaum ne hamari ye baat manney se inkar kar diya."
4687,"Abdur-Rehman-bin-Bishr-abdi ne hamein yahi hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Sufiyan ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Ismail-bin-Umayya ne Saeed-bin-abi-Saeed se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Yazeed-bin-Hurmuz se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : najda ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf khat likha . padhi. aur unhon-ne usi (pichhli hadis) ki tarah hadis bayan ki. Abu-Ishaq ne kaha : mujhey Abdur-Rehman-bin-Bishr ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Sufiyan ne poori yahi hadis bayan ki."
4688,"Qais-bin-Sad ne mujhey Yazeed-bin-Hurmuz se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : najda-bin-Aamir ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf khat likha to main us waqt , jab Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne uska khat padha aur iska jawab likha , unke paas hazir tha. Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Allah ki qism ! agar ye ( khayal ( na hota ke) ghaaliban ( main usey kisi qabeeh amal mein pad janey se rok loonga to usey jawab na likhtaa. ye uski aankhon ki khushi ke liye nahi. kaha : to unhon-ne uski taraf likha : tum ne rishteydaaron ke hissey ke barey mein puchha tha, jiska Allah ne zikr farmaya hai ke wo kon hain? to hamara khayal ye tha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke qaraabat daar ham hi log hain ( lekin) hamari qaum ne hamari baat manney se inkar kar diya aur tum ne yateem ke barey mein puchha tha, uski yateemii Kab khatm hoti hai? to jab wo nikah ki umr ko pahunch jaey, uske samajhdaar ho janey ka pata chalney lagey aur uska maal iske hawale kiya ja sakey to us se yateemii khatm ho jaeygi. aur tum ne puchha tha : kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mushrekeen ke bachchon mein se kisi ko qatl kartey they? to bila shubah Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unmein se kisi aik ko bhi qatl nahi kartey they aur tum bhi unmein se kisi ko qatl mat karnaa, siwaey-uske ke unke barey main tum ko bhi usi baat ka ilm ho jaey jiska us bachchey ke barey mein khizr (Alaihissalam) ko ilm hua jab unhon-ne usey qatl kiya tha. aur tum ne aurat aur ghulam ke barey mein puchha ke jab wo jang mein Sharik hon to kya unko bhi muqarrara hissey milega? waqia ye hai ke unka koi muqarrara hissey nahi, haan ye ke logon ki ghaneematon mein se unhein kuchh Atiya de diya jaey."
4689,"Mukhtar-bin-saifi ne Yazeed-bin-Hurmuz se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : najda ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf khat likha . padhi. aur unhon-ne hadis ka kuchh hissey bayan kiya aur unki tarah pura waqia bayan nahi kiya jinki hadisen ham ne ( uper ( bayan ki hain."
4690,"abdur-Raheem-bin-Sulaiman ne hamein Hisham (bin-Hassan ( se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hafsa binte-Sirin se aur unhon-ne Hazrat umme-Atiya ansariya (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath saat (7) ghazawaat mein Sharik hui, mein peechhey unke khemon mein rehti thi. unke liye khana taiyaar karti , zakhmiyon ki marham patti karti aur mareezon ki dekh bhaal karti thi."
4691,Yazid-bin-Harun ne Hisham-bin-Hassan se isi sanad ke sath isi tarah hadis bayan ki.
4692,"Shoba ne hamein Abu-Ishaq se hadis bayan ki ke) ibne-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf se Kufa ke ameer ( Abdullah-bin-Yazeed (bin-Husain ( logon ke sath barish ki dua maangney ke liye nikley to unhon-ne do rakatein padhein , phir barish ki dua ki. kaha is din meri mulaqat Hazrat Zaid-bin-Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) se hui. kaha : mere aur unke darmyan aik aadmi ke siwa koi na tha ya (kaha : ( mere aur unke darmyan ( bas ( aik aadmi tha to maine unse puchha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kitni jangein ki? unhon-ne kaha : unnees (19). to maine puchha : aap ne unke sath kitni jangein ladein ? unhon-ne kaha : satrah jangein . maine puchha : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka sabse pahlaa jang kon sa tha? unhon-ne kaha : zaatul-usair ya zaatul-ushair."
4693,"Zuhair ne hamein Abu-Ishaq se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Zaid-bin-Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) se ye hadis suni ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unnees ghazwey kiye aur hijrat ke baad aap ne sirf aik Haj kiya, iske siwa koi Haj nahi kiya, wo Hijjatul-wada tha."
4694,"Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath unnees ghazawaat mein shirkat ki. Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main badr aur uhud mein Sharik nahi hua, mujhey mere walid ne rok diya tha, jab ( mere walid ( Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) Uhud ke din Shahid ho gaey to (iske baad) main kisi bhi ghazwey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath shirkat karne se peechhey nahi raha."
4695,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Zaid-bin-Hubab ne hadis bayan ki, neez (isi ke saath) Saeed-bin-Muhammad Jarmi ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein abu-Tameela ne hadis bayan ki, un donon ( Zaid aur abu-Tameela ( ne kaha : hamein Husain-bin-Waqid ne Abdullah-bin-Barida se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unnees ghazwey kiye, aap ne unmein se aath (8) mein ladai ki Abu-Bakar ne ( unmein se) riwayat nahi kiya aur unhon-ne apni hadis mein kaha : mujhey Abdullah-bin-Barida ne hadis bayan ki."
4696,"Kahmas ne ibne-bareeda se aur unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha ke unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath sola ghazawaat mein shirkat ki."
4697,"hamein Muhammad-bin-Ibad ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Hatim-bin-Ismail ne Yazeed-bin-abi-Ubaid se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Salma (bin-Akwaa (Raziallahu anhu)) se suna, wo keh rahe they : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath saat (7) ghazawaat mein jang ki aur main un daston ke sath , jinhein aap rawaana farmatey they, nau (9) ghazawaat mein nikla . aik baar hamarey ameer Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) they aur aik baar Hazrat Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) . (pichhli hadis mein bayan ki hui tadaad sahi tar hai.)"
4698,"Qutaiba-bin-Saeed ne Hatim se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki, magar unhon-ne donon jagah saat (7) ghazawaat kahey ."
4699,"abu-Usama ne hamein bareed-bin-abi-burda se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu-Barda se aur unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik ghazwey mein nikley, ham chh: afraad they, ham sab ke liye oont aik ( hi ( tha, ham is par baari-baari sawar hotey they. kaha : hamarey pairon mein suraakh ho gaey, mere donon paon bhi zakhmi ho gaey aur mere naakhun gir gaey, ham apne paon par puraaney kapdon ke tukdey baandha kartey they, usi wjah se to us ghazwey ka naam zaatur-Riqaa' (dhajjiyon wali jang) pad gaya kyonke ham apne pairon par phatey puraaney kapdon ki dhajjiyaan baandha kartey they. abu-Barda ne kaha : Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye hadis bayan ki, phir usey ( bayan karne) ko na-pasand kiya jaisey wo ye baat na-pasand kartey hon ke unke amal ka koi aisa pahlu ho jiski unhon-ne tashheer (mash-hoor) ki ho. abu-Usama ne kaha : bareed ke ilawa kisi aur ne mujhey mazeed ye baat batai : aur Allah uski jazaa de."
4700,"Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bevi mohtarma Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) badr ki taraf nikley, jab aap Wabra ke Harra par pahunchey to aik aadmi aa kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se mila. uski jur'at aur bahaaduri ka bada charcha tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaba ne usey dekha to khush huey, jab wo aapko mila to usne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha : main isliye aaya hun ke aap ka sath dun aur aap ke sath ( ghaneemat mein se) hissey wsool karun. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se farmaya : kya tum Allah aur uske rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par eman rakhtey ho? usne kaha : nahi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : to lot jao, mein kisi mushrik se hargiz madad nahi loonga. (Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne) kaha : phir wo chala gaya, yahan tak ke jab ham darakht ke paas pahunchey to wo aadmi (doosri baar ( aapko mila aur aap se wahi baat kahi jo pehli martaba kahi thi, to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bhi us se wahi kuchh kaha jo pehli martaba kaha tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : wapas ho jao, mein kisi mushrik se hargiz madad nahi loonga. kaha : wo wapas chala gaya aur beida ke maqam par aapko mila to aap ne us se wahi baat poochhi jo pehli baar poochhi thi : tum Allah aur uske rasool par eman rakhtey ho? usne kaha : ji haan. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey farmaya : to phir ( hamarey saath) chalo."
